m%2Fsummerforpa%2Fstatus%2F1686355468602486784%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DO0vRZv_oqEQ3jXl1KSL4AQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpected%20to%20be%20higher%20than%20her%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20knows%20she%20is%20far%20from%20alone%20in%20that.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20that%20we're%20on-ramping%20millions%20of%20borrowers%C2%A0right%20back%20into%20a%20debt%20servitude%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20may%20have%20bought%20homes%20will%20now%20have%20to%20delay%20that%2C%20people%20who%20would%20have%20started%20families%20who%20will%20now%20have%20to%20think%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20doctors%2C%20to%20lawyers%2C%20to%20teachers%2C%20to%20social%20workers%2C%20people%20who%20are%20not%20going%20to%20pursue%20the%20passions%20that%20they%20have%2C%20or%20who%20are%20not%20going%20to%20fill%C2%A0positions%20that%20we%20need%2C%20because%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20deterred%20by%20seeing%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20for%20college%20graduates%20to%20survive%20and%20to%20contribute%20in%20our%20communities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20broad%20plan%20to%20cancel%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20student%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20federal%20borrowers.%20While%20the%20Education%20Department%20soon%20after%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-will-take-cancel-student-debt-higher-education-act-2023-7%5C%22%3Enew%20plan%20to%20enact%20relief%20using%20a%20different%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20ready%20in%20time%20for%20the%20payment%20resumption.%20To%20give%20borrowers%20some%20additional%20relief%2C%20the%20department%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A