%20dream'%2C%20India%20captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%20said%20in%20the%20video%20posted%20by%20BCCI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Destroying%20Culture%5C%22%3A%20Congress%20Slams%20New%20Uniform%20In%20Lakshadweep%20Schools%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20on%20Saturday%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20Lakshadweep%20administration's%20move%20to%20introduce%20a%20new%20pattern%20of%20uniform%20in%20schools%20in%20the%20union%20territory%2C%20and%20warned%20them%20of%20intense%20protests%2C%20including%20mass%20class%20boycott%20by%20students%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshadweep%20Congress%20leader%20and%20ex-MP%20Hamdullah%20Sayeed%20alleged%20that%20the%20new%20dress%20code%20directive%2C%20which%20is%20silent%20on%20hijabs%20or%20scarves%20for%20girl%20students%2C%20amounted%20to%20destroying%20the%20intrinsic%20culture%20and%20lifestyle%20of%20islanders%20in%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20archipelago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Lakshadweep%20administration%20were%20continuously%20attempting%20to%20implement%20anti-people%20policies%20that%20were%20totally%20against%20the%20culture%20and%20ethos%20of%20the%20islands%2C%20he%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20on%20the%20list%20was%20the%20recent%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Education%20Department%20introducing%20a%20new%20uniform%20code%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20accepted%20in%20any%20way%2C%20Mr%20Sayeed%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20allow%20any%20such%20directive%20that%20will%20destroy%20the%20culture%20and%20existing%20lifestyle%20of%20Lakshadweep.%20Such%20impositions%20are%20part%20of%20attempts%20to%20create%20unwanted%20tensions%20and%20issues%20in%20a%20democratic%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ex-MP%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20would%20launch%20a%20series%20of%20democratic%20agitations%20against%20the%20move%2C%20he%20said%20school%20students%20would%20boycott%20their%20classes%20to%20register%20their%20protest%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20said%20the%20Congress%20would%20also%20intensify%20its%20protests%20against%20the%20Lakshadweep%20administration's%20move%20to%20permit%20liquor%20outlets%20in%20the%20archipelago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20recently%20organised%20a%20mass%20protest%20march%20on%20various%20islands%20against%20the%20controversial%20move.%20A%20draft%20on%20the%20proposed%20Excise%20Regulation%20Bill%20was%20published%20by%20the%20Lakshadweep%20administration%20on%20August%203%20seeking%20suggestions%20from%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%2C%20which%20will%20permit%20the%20sale%20and%20consumption%20of%20liquor%20in%20the%20archipelago%2C%20has%20drawn%20widespread%20criticism%20from%20various%20corners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Lakshadweep%20MP%20and%20NCP%20leader%20Mohammed%20Faizal%20also%20indicated%20an%20intensifying%20protest%20against%20the%20draft%20liquor%20policy%20and%20the%20new%20uniform%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Mr%20Faizal%20urged%20the%20people%20of%20the%20islands%2C%20especially%20the%20parents'%20community%2C%20to%20resist%20any%20move%20by%20the%20administration%20to%20impose%20a%20hijab%20ban%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20new%20liquor%20policy%20and%20the%20uniform%20code%20as%20a%20violation%20of%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20he%20charged%20that%20the%20administration%20has%20pushed%20the%20islanders%20into%20an%20unprecedented%20crisis%20that%20they%20have%20never%20experienced%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20law%20is%20imposed%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20roots%20out%20the%20customs%2C%20religious%20beliefs%2C%20eating%20habits%2C%20and%20dressing%20patterns%20that%20have%20been%20followed%20by%20the%20islanders%20for%20ages%2C%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20protect%20the%20heritage%20and%20tradition%20of%20the%20archipelago%2C%20Mr%20Faizal%20urged%20everyone%20to%20stand%20united%20in%20the%20fight%20to%20protect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20row%20has%20erupted%20after%20the%20Lakshadweep%20administration%20introduced%20a%20new%20pattern%20of%20stitched%20school%20uniforms%2C%20including%20belts%2C%20ties%2C%20shoes%2C%20socks%2C%20etc.%2C%20for%20children%20studying%20in%20its%20schools%2C%20but%20its%20directive%20is%20silent%20on%20hijabs%20or%20scarves%20for%20girl%20students%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20circular%20dated%20August%2010%20issued%20to%20the%20principals%20and%20headmasters%20of%20the%20schools%20under%20the%20Lakshadweep%20administration%2C%20the%20Education%20department%20said%20school%20children%20wearing%20uniforms%20will%20ensure%20uniformity%20and%20also%20inculcate%20the%20spirit%20of%20discipline%20among%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWearing%20items%20other%20than%20prescribed%20uniform%20patterns%20will%20affect%20the%20concept%20of%20uniformity%20among%20school%20children.%20To%20maintain%20discipline%20and%20uniform%20dress%20code%20in%20schools%20are%20the%20responsibility%20of%20principals%20and%20heads%20of%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20circular%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20claimed%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20introduce%20a%20new%20pattern%20got%20appreciation%20from%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20students%2C%20parents%2C%20people's%20representatives%2C%20etc.%20and%20the%20Education%20Department%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20the%20same%20pattern%20for%20the%20current%20academic%20year%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20circular%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20directed%20all%20the%20principals%20and%20headmasters%20that%20every%20student%20attend%20the%20school%20in