20Bagula%20of%20the%20Nadia%20district.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20August%2010%2C%20his%20corpse%20returned%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwapnadeep%E2%80%99s%20body%20was%20found%20at%20the%20main%20boys%E2%80%99%20hostel%20of%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20institutions%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%209.%20Police%20said%20there%20were%20deep%20welts%20on%20his%20body.%20Many%20have%20suspected%20that%20while%20his%20death%20could%20have%20been%20made%20to%20look%20like%20suicide%2C%20Swapnadeep%20had%20actually%20been%20pushed%20from%20the%20third%20floor.%20He%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20brutal%20ragging%2C%20it%20has%20been%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwapnadeep%E2%80%99s%20father%20Ramprasad%20has%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20hostel%20residents%2C%20alleging%20murder.%20Late%20on%20Friday%2C%20August%2011%2C%20police%20arrested%20one%20Sourav%20Chowdhury%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20campus%E2%80%99s%20influential%20group%20Democratic%20Students%E2%80%99%20Federation.%20Chowdhury%20had%20studied%20Mathematics%20at%20JU%20but%20had%20already%20got%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20and%20had%20been%20staying%20on%20at%20the%20hostel.%20Herein%20lies%20one%20of%20the%20chief%20reasons%20why%20anger%20has%20poured%20out%20over%20this%20death.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfreen%20Begum%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Students%20Federation%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20in%20power%20in%20the%20Arts%20students%E2%80%99%20union%20of%20JU%20(under%20which%20the%20Bengali%20department%20falls)%20%E2%80%93%20says%20that%20students%20like%20Chowdhury%20wield%20enormous%20power%20in%20the%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20departments.%20And%20because%20these%20students%20are%20more%20in%20number%20at%20the%20hostel%2C%20there%20is%20little%20any%20new%20student%20can%20do%20to%20escape%20their%20elaborate%20ragging%20rituals.%20So%20powerful%20is%20the%20network%20of%20former%20students%20at%20the%20hostel%20that%20some%20reports%20have%20it%20that%20when%20police%20first%20attempted%20to%20visit%20the%20hostel%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20discovery%20of%20Swapnadeep%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20hostel%20residents%20initially%20tried%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20entering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20students%20claim%20to%20be%20politically%20neutral%20but%20are%20anything%20but.%20Many%20join%20Trinamool%20Congress%20or%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20after%20graduating%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Afreen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20JU%20physics%20professor%20Partha%20Pratim%20Roy%2C%20who%20represents%20the%20JU%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Association%2C%20visited%20the%20hostel%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20he%20says%20he%20saw%20several%20first-year%20students%20all%20sporting%20the%20same%20haircut%20%E2%80%93%20an%20indication%20that%20they%20had%20all%20been%20victims%20of%20ragging.%20JUTA%20has%20asked%20that%20former%20students%20be%20immediately%20removed%20from%20the%20hostel%20and%20that%20first-year%20students%20be%20housed%20separately.%20The%20latter%20has%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20happened%20yesterday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERagging%20is%20banned%20on%20the%20JU%20campus%2C%20but%20the%20institution%E2%80%99s%20history%20of%20tackling%20it%20is%20not%20pristine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJU%3A%20In%20the%20eye%20of%20a%20bigger%20political%20storm%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAction%20against%20ragging%2C%20as%20a%20source%20puts%20it%2C%20depends%20on%20the%20decisions%20of%20a%20self-appointed%20political%20elite%20and%20not%20on%20the%20admin%20itself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20then%20V-C%20Souvik%20Bhattacharya%20resigned%20after%20students%20gheraoed%20him%20and%20other%20officials%20demanding%20the%20revocation%20of%20punishment%20given%20to%20two%20students%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20ragging%20incident.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Roy%20says%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20elected%20representatives%20in%20various%20administrative%20positions%20has%20led%20to%20a%20breakdown%20in%20dialogue%20between%20students%2C%20teachers%20and%20administration.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20university%20professors%20have%20written%20of%20a%20sense%20of%20collective%20failure%20at%20the%20death%20of%20a%20student%20in%20this%20manner.%20At%20least%20two%20teachers%20in%20the%20Arts%20faculty%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20were%20deeply%20disturbed%20and%20could%20not%20speak%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Feducation-today%2Fnews%2Fstory%2Fjadavpur-university-without-a-vc-from-june-1-2387627-2023-06-01%5C%22%3EVice-Chancellor%20at%20JU%20since%20June%201%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJU%20has%20long%20since%20been%20the%20flashpoint%20of%20a%20struggle%20between%20its%20students%2C%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20administration%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20(the%20Bengal%20governor%2C%20appointed%20by%20the%20Union%20is%20its%20Chancellor)%20over%20efforts%20to%20control%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20institution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20significant%20annoyance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbengal-school-recruitment-scam-1911-lose-jobs-more-on-the-cards%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20lack%20of%20opportunities%20for%20the%20young%20in%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20incident%20has%20also%20stirred%20conversation%20on%20an%20essential%20divide%20which%20liberal%20campuses%20like%20JU%20are%20loathe%20to%20acknowledge%20%E2%80%93%20between%20poor%20students%20and%20rich%2C%20and%20between%20students%20studying%20certain%20subjects%20and%20those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EVulnerable%20to%20ragging%20despite%20ban%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwapnadeep%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20especially%20vulnerable.%20His%20%E2%80%98disadvantages%E2%80%99%20were%20many.%20He%20chose%20Bengali%20%E2%80%93%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98soft%E2%80%99%20option%20against%20even%20Arts%20subjects%20like%20English%20and%20even%20more%20when%20compared%20to%20Science%20or%20Engineering%2C%20especially%20for%20men.%20He%20came%20from%20a%20faraway%20district.%20And%20he%20had%20no%20immediate%20friends%20or%20relatives%20in%20Kolkata%20to%20whose%20houses%20he%20could%20escape%20when%20the%20alleged%20ragging%20took%20place%20in%20the%20hostel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20former%20students%20%E2%80%93%20on%20social%20media%20and%20in%20local%20news%20channels%20%E2%80%93%20have%20pointed%20out%20how%20they%20were%20compelled%20to%20leave%20the%20hostel%20when%20faced%20with%20ragging%20and%20live%20in%20nearby%20%E2%80%98messes%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20could%20only%20do%20so%20because%20they%20had%20the%20money%20to.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwapnadeep%2C%20whose%20father%20is%20a%20cooperative%20bank%20employee%20and%20whose%20mother%20is%20an%20ASHA%20worker%2C%20had%20been%20enthusiastic%20about%20his%20first%20few%20classes%20at%20the%20Bengali%20department%20on%20the%20day%20of%20his%20death.%20He%20spoke%20happily%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20at%205.30%20pm%2C%20she%20recounted.%20But%20by%209.30%20pm%2C%20in%20a%20phone%20call%2C%20he%20was%20in%20tears%20and%20asked%20to%20be%20taken%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20turn%20of%20events%20has%20not%20only%20been%20shocking%20but%20deepened%20distrust%20of%20an%20institution%20otherwise%20known%20for%20its%20free-thinking%20campus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Bagula%2C%20one%20Ramkrishna%20Ghosh%20tells%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20it%20is%20scary%20that%20%E2%80%9C