ng%20against%20our%20partners%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20quite%20understand%20our%20situation%20and%20how%20we%20are%20fighting%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20intelligence%20sergeant%20in%20the%2041st%20Mechanised%20Brigade%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BDutchman%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20openDemocracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2063%2C000%20Ukrainian%20troops%20have%20been%20trained%20in%20the%20West%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Germany%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20go%20through%20a%2035-day%20%26quot%3Bcrash%20course%26quot%3B%20of%20basic%20soldier%20training%2C%20a%20UK%20source%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Reynolds%2C%20a%20land%20warfare%20expert%20at%20the%20UK-based%20defense%20think%20tank%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20(RUSI)%2C%20said%20that%20the%20training%20provided%20by%20the%20West%20was%20safer%20but%20less%20comparable%20to%20actual%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20health%20and%20safety%20regulation.%20Yet%20this%20means%20they%20are%20going%20on%20to%20the%20battlefield%20less%20prepared%2C%26quot%3B%20Reynolds%20told%20openDemocracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20this%20strategy%20may%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20things%20going%20wrong%20during%20live%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDutchman%26quot%3B%20said%20that%20while%20NATO%20training%20can%20be%20useful%20for%20things%20like%20shooting%20and%20learning%20to%20use%20equipment%2C%20most%20major%20combat%20training%20occurred%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20limitation%20is%20that%20Western%20armies%20have%20been%20focused%20on%20fighting%20insurgencies%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20Ukraine's%2041st%20Brigade%20said%20that%20NATO%20instructors%20often%20used%20examples%20from%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20which%20largely%20involved%20clearing%20houses%20and%20identifying%20insurgents%20among%20the%20locals%2C%20which%20they%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20really%20relevant%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222649%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Marine%20scouts%20of%20the%201st%20Light%20Armored%20Reconnaissance%20company%20clearing%20a%20house%20November%2020%2C%202004%20in%20Fallujah%2C%20Iraq.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d73d315e5d5a00195cc6f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221987%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Peterson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDutchman%26quot%3B%20said%20that%20Western%20instructors%20have%20experience%20in%20urban%20warfare%2C%20fighting%20in%20cities%20and%20towns%20%E2%80%94%20but%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20much%20of%20the%20fighting%20is%20on%20flat%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20people%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20effectively%20clear%20trenches%2C%20enter%20them%2C%20how%20to%20throw%20grenades%20effectively%2C%20how%20not%20to%20trip%20on%20booby%20traps%2C%20to%20understand%20what%20grenades%20the%20%5BRussians%5D%20throw%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%20to%20understand%20the%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20instructors%20also%20typically%20planned%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20weaker%20enemy%20in%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Dutchman%20said%2C%20as%20NATO%20forces%20sought%20to%20overwhelm%20their%20enemies%20with%20the%20type%20of%20firepower%20that%20Ukraine%20does%20not%20possess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20limitation%20is%20that%20NATO%20health%20and%20safety%20regulations%20require%20troops%20to%20undergo%20basic%20training%20before%20moving%20on%20to%20more%20advanced%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20due%20to%20time%20constraints%2C%20Ukrainian%20troops%20often%20don't%20reach%20those%20levels%2C%20Reynolds%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20legal%2C%20regulatory%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20permissions%20perspective%2C%20we%20can't%20do%20%5Bthe%20type%20of%20training%20Ukrainians%20want%5D%20unless%20we%20make%20some%20fairly%20serious%20policy%20changes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20significant%20upside%20of%20the%20Western%20training%20is%20that%20Ukrainian%20troops%20take%20home%20expensive%20equipment%2C%20including%20body%20armor%20and%20medical%20supplies%2C%20a%20source%20involved%20in%20the%20UK%20training%20process%20told%20openDemocracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-troops-left-underprepared-by-nato-training-report-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691829964000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63d3fc774589790018e57b43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-troops-left-underprepared-by-nato-training-report-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20say%20that%20Western%20instructors%20focus%20is%20fighting%20insurgencies%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20lack%20experience%20in%20facing%20an%20enemy%20like%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-troops-left-underprepared-by-nato-training-report-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Not%20true%5C%22%3A%20Virat%20Kohli%20on%20reported%20social%20media%20earnings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691829953000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102674639%2Cimgsize-36100.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Foff-the-field%2Fvirat-kohli-on-reported-social-media-earnings%2Farticleshow%2F102674529.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20star%20batsman%20Virat%20Kohli%20on%20Saturday%20clarified%20that%20the%20reports%20regarding%20his%20