tory%2Famp%2Fat-least-one-person-dead-and-dozens-rescued-as-migrant-boat-crossing-channel-capsizes-12938447%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fat-least-one-person-dead-and-dozens-rescued-as-migrant-boat-crossing-channel-capsizes-12938447%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20to%20watch%20on%20OTT%20this%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691829000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102640791%2Cimgsize-32362.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fheart-of-stone-made-in-heaven-and-others-what-to-watch-on-ott-this-week%2Farticleshow%2F102640858.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102640858.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThis%20week%20seems%20to%20be%20like%20Super%20Bowl%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20content%20on%20OTT.%20From%20Alia%20Bhatt's%20big%20Hollywood%20debut%20Heart%20of%20Stone%20to%20the%20hugely%20awaited%20Made%20In%20Heaven%20Season%202%2C%20it%20is%20all%20there.%20To%20add%20more%2C%20there%20is%20some%20action%20and%20a%20documentary%20too.%20Have%20a%20look%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fheart-of-stone-made-in-heaven-and-others-what-to-watch-on-ott-this-week%2Farticleshow%2F102640858.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Wrestling%20Federation%20Polls%20Have%20Been%20Put%20On%20Hold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20on%20Friday%20put%20on%20hold%20the%20much-anticipated%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20elections%2C%20which%20were%20scheduled%20for%20today%2C%20following%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Wrestling%20Association%20(HWA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%2C%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Vinod%20S%20Bhardwaj%2C%20postponed%20the%20case%20until%20August%2028%2C%20following%20a%20petition%20from%20the%20HWA%20challenging%20the%20decision%20to%20allow%20the%20Haryana%20Amateur%20Wrestling%20Association%20(HAWA)%20to%20cast%20votes%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho's%20Who%20Of%20Haryana%20Wrestling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20groups%20that%20claim%20to%20be%20the%20governing%20body%20of%20wrestling%20in%20Haryana.%20Under%20the%20WFI%20rules%20and%20constitution%2C%20any%20registered%20affiliated%20body%20is%20entitled%20to%20send%20two%20representatives%20to%20cast%20votes%20in%20WFI%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Deepinder%20Hooda-led%20Haryana%20Wrestling%20Association%20(HWA)%20says%20that%20it%20is%20a%20registered%20society%20that%20is%20affiliated%20to%20the%20WFI%20-%20the%20premier%20governing%20body%20for%20wrestling%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20body%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Amateur%20Wrestling%20Association%20(HAWA)%2C%20also%20claims%20to%20be%20affiliated%20with%20both%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20and%20the%20Haryana%20Olympic%20Association%20(HOA)%20-%20despite%20the%20HOA's%20counsel%20in%20the%20case%20telling%20the%20High%20Court%20that%20the%20HAWA%20is%20not%20an%20affiliated%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHAWA%20further%20asserts%20that%20it%20would%20be%20illegal%20for%20the%20HWA%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20election%20process%20because%20it%20is%20not%20affiliated%20with%20the%20WFI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20returning%20officer%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20WFI%20elections%20chose%20two%20members%20from%20the%20HAWA%20as%20Haryana's%20representatives%20for%20the%20Electoral%20College.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20challenged%20the%20returning%20officer's%20order%20in%20the%20HC%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Haryana%20Amateur%20Wrestling%20Association%20may%20be%20affiliated%20with%20the%20WFI%20but%20it%20is%20not%20affiliated%20with%20the%20HOA%2C%20meaning%20they%20are%20not%20entitled%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20poll%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ravinder%20Malik%2C%20representing%20HWA%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternal%20Turmoil%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20and%20former%20WFI%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20embroiled%20in%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20case%20after%20several%20women%20wrestlers%20levelled%20allegations%20against%20him%2C%20is%20ineligible%20to%20contest%20the%20election%20because%20he%20has%20served%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20federation%20for%2012%20years%2C%20which%20is%20the%20maximum%20period%20allowed%20under%20the%20National%20Sports%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBesides%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20charges%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20is%20also%20facing%20flak%20from%20several%20state%20wrestling%20bodies%20who%20have%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20disaffiliated%20from%20the%20WFI%20during%20his%2012-year%20term%20as%20its%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Singh%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20control%20the%20WFI%20through%20proxies%2C%20as%2018%20of%20his%20supporters%20filed%20nominations%20on%20July%2031.%20His%C2%A0panel%20includes%20one%20candidate%20for%20the%20federation's%20president%2C%20six%20for%20vice%20president%2C%20seven%20for%20executive%20members%2C%20two%20for%20joint%20secretary%2C%20one%20for%20secretary%20general%2C%20and%20one%20for%20the%20treasurer%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association's%20(IOA)%20ad-hoc%20panel%20governing%20the%20WFI%20had%20initially%20scheduled%20the%20elections%20for%20July%206.%20However%2C%20the%20panel%20was%20forced%20to%20reschedule%20the%20polls%20to%20July%2011%20after%20five%20disaffiliated%20state%20bodies%20from%20Haryana%2C%20Telanganam%20Maharashtra%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20approached%20the%20panel%20for%20a%20hearing%2C%20claiming%20that%20their%20dismissal%20was%20unjustified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20the%20Assam%20Wrestling%20Association%20(AWA)%20sought%20the%20right%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20WFI%20elections%2C%20forcing%20the%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20to%20stay%20the%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20July%2011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20then%20allowed%20the%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20on%20August%2012%2C%20putting%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20order%20before%20yesterday's%20developments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho's%20In%20Fray%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2024%20candidates%20vying%20for%2015%20spots%20on%20the%20WFI%20Executive%20Committee.%202010%20Commonwealth%20Games%20gold%20medallist%20Anita%20Sheoran%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20vice-president%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Wrestling%20Association%20and%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20are%20the%20top%20candidates%20for%20the%20president's%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20from%20Haryana%20and%20employed%20with%20the%20state%20police%2C%20Ms%20Sheoran%20filed%20her%20nomination%20as%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20Odisha%20unit%20for%20the%20WFI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sheoran%20has%20the%20backing%20of%20some%20of%20India's%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20who%20spearheaded%20the%20wrestlers'%20protest%20at%20New%20Delhi's%20Jantar%20Mantar%2C%20demanding%20the%20arrest%20of%20Mr%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20elected%2C%20she%20will%20become%20the%20first%20female%20president%20of%20the%20WFI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691828640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fvnnma0d8_brij-bhushan-ani-650_650x400_07_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushan-singh-wrestling-federation-of-india-explained-why-wrestling-federation-polls-have-been-put-on-hold-4292155%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20on%20Friday%20put%20on%20hold%20the%20much-anticipated%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20elections%2C%20which%20were%20scheduled%20for%20today%2C%20following%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Wrestling%20Association%20(HWA).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushan-singh-wrestling-federation-of-india-explained-why-wrestling-federation-polls-have-been-put-on-hold-4292155%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Never%20Clear%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Anti-NEET%20Bill%2C%20Entrance%20To%20Stay%3A%20Governor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20today%20categorically%20asserted%20he%20will%20never%20clear%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government's%20anti-NEET%20bill%2C%20even%20as%20it%20was%20now%20awaiting%20Presidential%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20achievements%20without%20the%20National%20Entrance-cum-Eligibility%20Test%20(NEET)%20were%20not%20enough%20for%20the%20future%2C%20Governor%20Ravi%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20qualifying%20test%20is%20here%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20will%20be%20the%20last%20man%20to%20give%20clearance%3B%20never%2C%20ever.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20my%20children%20to%20feel%20intellectually%20disabled.%20I%20want%20our%20children%20to%20compete%20and%20be%20the%20best.%20They%20have%20proved%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20categorical%20statement%20came%20during%20an%20interaction%20with%20top%20NEET%20scorers%20in%20UG-2023%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20here%20when%20a%20parent%20sought%20for%20the%20Governor's%20%26quot%3Bclearance%20to%20ban%20NEET%2C%26quot%3B%20an%