ight%20be%20possible%20is%20patently%20contrary%20to%20the%20lessons%20of%20recent%20history.%20Some%20necessary%20accommodation%20to%20address%20the%20sense%20of%20disquiet%20%E2%80%93%20legitimate%20or%20otherwise%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20majority%20makes%20sense%2C%20but%20continuing%20down%20that%20path%20to%20rewrite%20history%20will%20be%20disastrous%20for%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20the%20people%2C%20captured%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstandably%2C%20there%20is%20talk%20amongst%20minority%20citizens%20about%20what%20short-term%20and%20long-term%20communication%20strategies%20to%20adopt%20for%20a%20working%20relationship%20with%20the%20government%20and%20the%20majority%20they%20claim%20to%20represent.%20Periodically%20some%20people%20have%20taken%20the%20initiative%20to%20join%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmuslim-intellectuals-mohan-bhagwat-dialogue-or-monologues%5C%22%3Edialogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20high%20functionaries%20of%20the%20government%20and%20leadership%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20with%20uncertain%20results%20beyond%20photo%20ops%20and%20well-meaning%20press%20statements.%20Others%20have%20gone%20further%20to%20secure%20membership%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20have%20even%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fonly-one-party-wins-when-indian-muslims-defend-the-bjp%5C%22%3Enominated%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmuslims-must-dialogue-with-all-indians-except-those-who-dream-of-their-disenfranchisement%5C%22%3EMuslims%20Must%20Dialogue%20with%20All%20Indians%2C%20Except%20Those%20Who%20Dream%20of%20Their%20Disenfranchisement%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20adds%20to%20the%20support%20the%20BJP%20establishment%20has%20had%20for%20some%20time%20from%20conspicuous%20political%20persons%2C%20as%20indeed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farif-mohammad-khan-kerala-governor%5C%22%3Eincumbent%20governor%20of%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Muslim%20institutions%20whose%20heads%20have%20shown%20implicit%20or%20explicit%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20have%20added%20precious%20little%20to%20a%20larger%20conversation%20as%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20institutional%20following%20are%20cynical%20about%20such%20efforts%2C%20dismissing%20them%20as%20opportunist%20overtures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20minority%20universities%20are%20willy-nilly%20showing%20compliance%20to%20the%20wishes%20of%20political%20bosses.%20It%20might%20be%20too%20early%20to%20estimate%20the%20cost%20of%20all%20this%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%20and%20integrity%20of%20thinking%20of%20faculty%20and%20student%20body.%20Meanwhile%2C%20protests%20have%20become%20difficult%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%2C%20as%20many%20students%20discovered%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20CAA-NRC%20demonstrations%20in%20different%20cities%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20cannot%20reject%20dialogue%20entirely%20and%20hope%20that%20both%20sides%20engage%20in%20it%20with%20honest%20intentions%20and%20sincerity.%20Better%20understanding%20of%20each%20other%20is%20the%20purpose%20of%20dialogue%20and%20that%20might%20reduce%20suspicions%20and%20misplaced%20fear.%20But%20for%20successful%20inter-faith%20dialogue%2C%20an%20element%20of%20internal%20dialogue%20in%20the%20community%20might%20be%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20cannot%20forget%20that%20our%20present%20condition%20is%20largely%20caused%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20internal%20dialogue%20ensured%20by%20the%20political%20ambitions%20of%20individuals%20and%20political%20outfits.%20Of%20course%2C%20before%20venturing%20to%20resume%20dialogue%20within%20the%20community%2C%20we%20may%20first%20need%20to%20reassess%20the%20performance%20of%20those%20we%20trusted%20over%20the