young%20kid%2C%20has%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20domestic%20cricket.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20quality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20has%20played%20a%20Test%20and%20three%20ODIs%20and%20T20Is%20each%20on%20this%20tour.%20In%20Tests%2C%20he%20has%20picked%20two%20wickets.%20In%20ODIs%2C%20he%20has%20four%20wickets%20with%20the%20best%20figures%20of%203%2F30%20while%20in%20T20Is%2C%20he%20has%20two%20wickets%20with%20the%20best%20figures%20of%201%2F19.%20The%2029-year-old%20represents%20Bengal%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20wicket%20at%20the%20Central%20Broward%20Regional%20Park%20Stadium%20Turf%20Ground%2C%20Lauderhill%2C%20Paras%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20good%20batting%20surface%2C%20with%20the%20ball%20coming%20on%20the%20bat%20nicely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20different%20(As%20compared%20to%20pitches%20earlier%20in%20the%20series)%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20soil.%20It%20is%20black%20soil%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20we%20get%20in%20North%20India.%20It%20is%20a%20good%20wicket%2C%20will%20be%20nice%20to%20bat%20on%2C%20with%20the%20ball%20coming%20to%20the%20bat%20nicely.%20That%20is%20what%20we%20saw%20in%20the%20nets.%20Stroke-making%20was%20easy.%20It%20could%20be%20a%20high-scoring%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParas%20said%20that%20it%20is%20good%20to%20be%20in%20the%20US%20because%20of%20the%20crowd%20support%20and%20reception%20for%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20conversations%20with%20the%20bowling%20unit%20about%20playing%20on%20a%20batting-friendly%20surface%2C%20the%20coach%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20format%20is%20such%20that%20batters%20are%20going%20to%20come%20after%20you%2C%20especially%20on%20a%20wicket%20like%20this.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20have%20discipline.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20decide%20on%20plans%2C%20the%20execution%20becomes%20really%20important.%20If%20you%20focus%20on%20it%2C%20you%20are%20giving%20yourself%20the%20best%20chance%20to%20be%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParas%20also%20expressed%20happiness%20with%20the%20way%20the%20team%20bounced%20back%20in%20the%20third%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20extremely%20happy%20with%20the%20way%20we%20have%20come%20back.%20Even%20in%20the%20first%20two%20games%2C%20we%20were%20not%20much%20behind.%20We%20just%20could%20not%20seize%20the%20opportunities.%20Had%20we%20done%20so%2C%20results%20could%20have%20been%20different.%20The%20way%20we%20played%20the%20third%20T20I%2C%20we%20tick%20all%20the%20boxes%20across%20all%20the%20departments.%20We%20are%20only%20going%20to%20go%20up%20from%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691824740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fh3cbel7g_india_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ftwo-star-indian-batter-will-soon-be-assigned-bowling-roles-in-the-indian-cricket-team-they-are-4292013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Soon%2C%20new%20roles%20may%20be%20assigned%20to%20two%20talented%20youngsters%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ftwo-star-indian-batter-will-soon-be-assigned-bowling-roles-in-the-indian-cricket-team-they-are-4292013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ftwo-star-indian-batter-will-soon-be-assigned-bowling-roles-in-the-indian-cricket-team-they-are-4292013%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ftwo-star-indian-batter-will-soon-be-assigned-bowling-roles-in-the-indian-cricket-team-they-are-4292013%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Says%20Hate%20Speech%20Unacceptable%2C%20Asks%20Centre%20To%20Constitute%20Committee%20To%20Look%20Into%20Cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F22114407%2Fsupreme-court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%2C%20August%2012%2C%20said%20that%20the%20problem%20of%20hate%20speech%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20good%20and%20nobody%20can%20accept%20it%E2%80%9D%2C%20asking%20a%20committee%20led%20by%20the%20director%20general%20of%20police%20(DGP)%20to%20examine%20complaints%20and%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20allegations%20of%20such%20speeches%20made%20in%20Haryana%20following%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20the%20top%20court%20observed%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Charmony%20and%20comity%E2%80%9D%20between%20communities%20and%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20constitute%20a%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20made%20these%20observations%20during%20the%20resumed%20hearing%20of%20a%20plea%20seeking%20action%20against%20those%20who%20called%20for%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20boycott%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20following%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaheen%20Abdulla%2C%20who%20filed%20the%20plea%2C%20relied%20on%20a%20video%20in%20which%20an%20organisation%20on%20August%202%20warned%20residents%20and%20shopkeepers%20of%20boycott%20if%20they%20continue%20to%20employ%20any%20Muslims.%20The%20video%20was%20from%20a%20neighbourhood%20in%20Hisar%2C%20Haryana%20and%20police%20officials%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20stated%20that%20such%20calls%20not%20only%20%E2%80%9Cdemonise%20communities%20and%20openly%20call%20for%20violence%E2%80%9D%20but%20also%20would%20%E2%80%9Cinevitably%20lead%20to%20communal%20disharmony%20and%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fcall-for-boycott-of-muslims-unacceptable-hate-speech-needs-to-end-supreme-court%2Farticleshow%2F102659631.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20S.V.N.%20Bhatti%20asked%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20K.M.%20Nataraj%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20to%20seek%20instructions%20and%20inform%20it%20about%20the%20committee%20by%20August%2018.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20to%20be%20harmony%20and%20comity%20between%20the%20communities.%20All%20the%20communities%20are%20responsible.%20The%20problem%20of%20hate%20speech%20is%20not%20good%20and%20nobody%20can%20accept%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20directed%20the%20petitioner%20to%20collate%20all%20the%20material%2C%20including%20video%2C%20and%20submit%20them%20to%20the%20nodal%20officers%20appointed%20in%20pursuance%20to%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20October%202022%20judgment%20on%20hate%20speeches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20hate%20speeches%20vitiate%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20said%20that%20wherever%20required%2C%20adequate%20police%20force%20or%20paramilitary%20force%20would%20be%20deployed%20and%20the%20authorities%2C%20including%20the%20police%2C%20will%20use%20CCTV%20cameras%20installed%20or%20record%2Fmake%20video%20recordings%20in%20all%20sensitive%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ET%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20suggested%20that%20a%20DGP-led%20committee%20of%20three-four%20police%20officers%20%E2%80%93%20nominated%20by%20the%20DGP%20%E2%80%93%20examine%20complaints%20and%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20allegations.%20If%20found%20true%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdirections%20can%20be%20issued%20to%20the%20police%20authorities%20to%20act%20against%20the%20miscreants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20the%20Union%20government%20said%20the%20government%20does%20not%20support%20hate%20speech.%20The%20counsel%20added%20that%20in%20some%20places%20the%20mechanism%20to%20tackle%20hate%20speech%20was%20not%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691824553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F22114407%2Fsupreme-court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-hate-speech-unacceptable-centre-committee-haryana-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20made%20these%20observations%20during%20the%20resumed%20hearing%20of%20a%20plea%20seeking%20action%20against%20those%20who%20called%20for%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20boycott%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20following%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-hate-speech-unacceptable-centre-committee-haryana-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Khooni%20Khel%20Khela%20Hai%5C%22%3A%20PM%20Attacks%20Trinamool%20Over%20Bengal%20Poll%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20violence%20during%20Panchayat%20polls%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Saturday%20alleged%20that%20the%20ruling%20Mamata-Banerjee%20Trinamool%20Congress%20had%20%26quot%3Bplayed%20with%20blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTMC%20ne%20khooni%20khel%20khela%20hai...%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20Hindi%20while%20addressing%20the%20Kshetriya%20Panchayati%20Raj%20Parishad%20in%20West%20Bengal%20via%20videoconferencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20threatening%20voters%20and%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20their%20life%20hell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20anything%20required%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20BJP%20candidate%20can%20file%20nomination...they%20not%20only%20threaten%20BJP%20workers%20but%20also%20the%20voters.%20Contracts%20are%20given%20out%20to%20capture%20booths...This%20is%20their%20way%20of%20doing%20politics%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20alleged%20that%20TMC%20gave%20contracts%20to%20goons%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20capture%20the%20booth%20on%20the%20vote-counting%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20party%20had%20given%20a%20contract%20to%20goons%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20capture%20booths%20on%20the%20vote%20counting%20day.%20During%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20the%20TMC%20forced%20BJP%20members%20out%20of%20office%20and%20did%20not%20let%20them%20even%20watch.%20When%20BJP%20won%20despite%20all%20this%2C%20they%20took%20out%20rallies%20against%20our%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanchayat%20elections%20in%20West%20Bengal%20took%20place%20on%20July%208%20and%20counting%20of%20the%20votes%20for%2063%2C229%20-Gram%20Panchayat%20seats%20took%20place%20on%20July%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%20has%20won%20in%2028%2C985%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%207%2C764%20seats%20while%20Congress%20has%20secured%202%2C022%20seats%20so%20far.%20TMC%20was%20leading%20on%201%2C540%20panchayat%20seats%20while%20BJP%20was%20leading%20on%20417%2C%20according%20to%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunist%20Party%20of%20India-Marxist%20(CPI-M)%20has%20won%202%2C409%20seats%20and%20is%20leading%20in%20260%20seats.%20Other%20parties%20won%20725%20seats%20and%20leading%20on%2023%20seats%2C%20while%20independents%20which%20included%20TMC%20rebels%20won%201%2C656%20seats%20and%20are%20maintaining%20a%20led%20in%20104%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20voting%20day%20was%20marred%20with%20widespread%20violence%2C%20looting%20of%20ballots%20papers%20and%20rigging.%20There%20were%20reports%20of%20booth%20capturing%2C%20damaging%20of%20ballot%20boxes%20an