.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-and-wife-shabana-turn-producers-with-bhaiyaaji%2Farticleshow%2F102672619.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Surveillance%20Cams%20That%20Can%20Detect%20Skin%20Color%20Raise%20Rights%20Concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChinese%20surveillance%20equipment%20maker%20Dahua%20is%20selling%20cameras%20with%20what%20it%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bskin%20colour%20analytics%26quot%3B%20feature%20in%20Europe%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20IPVM%20(Internet%20Protocol%20Video%20Market)%2C%20a%20US-based%20security%20and%20surveillance%20industry%20research%20group%2C%20as%20cited%20by%20Voice%20of%20America.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20July%2031%20IPVM%20report%20accessed%20by%20VOA%20Mandarin%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20company%20defended%20the%20analytics%20as%20being%20a%20'basic%20feature%20of%20a%20smart%20security%20solution.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoA%20is%20the%20state-owned%20news%20network%20and%20international%20radio%20broadcaster%20of%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20which%20produces%20digital%2C%20TV%2C%20and%20radio%20content%20that%20is%20shared%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20IPVM%20and%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20reported%20that%20Dahua%20provided%20a%20video%20surveillance%20system%20with%20%26quot%3Breal-time%20Uyghur%20warnings%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Chinese%20police%20that%20included%20eyebrow%20size%2C%20skin%20colour%20and%20ethnicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIPVM's%202018%20statistical%20report%20shows%20that%20since%202016%2C%20Dahua%20and%20another%20Chinese%20video%20surveillance%20company%2C%20Hikvision%2C%20have%20won%20contracts%20worth%20USD%201%20billion%20from%20the%20government%20of%20China's%20Xinjiang%20province%2C%20a%20centre%20of%20Uyghur%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDahua's%20ICC%20Open%20Platform%20guide%20for%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20body%20characteristics%26quot%3B%20includes%20%26quot%3Bskin%20colour%2Fcomplexion%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20In%20what%20Dahua%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bdata%20dictionary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20says%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bskin%20colour%20types%26quot%3B%20that%20Dahua%20analytic%20tools%20would%20target%20are%20%26quot%3Byellow%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bblack%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwhite.%26quot%3B%20VOA%20Mandarin%20verified%20this%20on%20Dahua's%20Chinese%20website%2C%20VOA%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPVM%20report%20also%20says%20that%20skin%20colour%20detection%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BPersonnel%20Control%26quot%3B%20category%2C%20a%20feature%20Dahua%20touts%20as%20part%20of%20its%20Smart%20Office%20Park%20solution%20intended%20to%20provide%20security%20for%20large%20corporate%20campuses%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%20what%20these%20video%20analytics%20do%20is%20that%2C%20if%20you%20turn%20them%20on%2C%20then%20the%20camera%20will%20automatically%20try%20and%20determine%20the%20skin%20colour%20of%20whoever%20passes%2C%20whoever%20it%20captures%20in%20the%20video%20footage%2C%26quot%3B%20VOA%20quoted%20Charles%20Rollet%2C%20the%20co-author%20of%20the%20IPVM%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that%20means%20the%20camera%20is%20going%20to%20be%20guessing%20or%20attempting%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20person%20in%20front%20of%20it%20%E2%80%A6%20has%20black%2C%20white%20or%20yellow%2C%20in%20their%20words%2C%20skin%20colour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPVM%20report%20said%20that%20Dahua%20is%20selling%20cameras%20with%20the%20skin%20colour%20analytics%20feature%20in%20three%20European%20nations.%20Each%20has%20a%20recent%20history%20of%20racial%20tension%2C%20Germany%2C%20France%20and%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDahua%20said%20its%20skin%20tone%20analysis%20capability%20was%20an%20essential%20function%20in%20surveillance%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20IPVM%2C%20Dahua%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20platform%20in%20question%20is%20entirely%20consistent%20with%20our%20commitments%20to%20not%20build%20solutions%20that%20target%20any%20single%20racial%2C%20ethnic%2C%20or%20national%20group.%20The%20ability%20to%20generally%20identify%20observable%20characteristics%20such%20as%20height%2C%20weight%2C%20hair%20and%20eye%20colour%2C%20and%20general%20categories%20of%20skin%20colour%20is%20a%20basic%20feature%20of%20a%20smart%20security%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIPMV%20said%20the%20company%20has%20previously%20denied%20offering%20the%20mentioned%20feature%2C%20and%20colour%20detection%20is%20uncommon%20in%20mainstream%20surveillance%20tech%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20Western%20nations%2C%20there%20has%20long%20been%20a%20controversy%20over%20errors%20due%20to%20skin%20colour%20in%20surveillance%20technologies%20for%20facial%20recognition.%20Identifying%20skin%20colour%20in%20surveillance%20applications%20raises%20human%20rights%20and%20civil%20rights%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20unusual%20to%20see%20it%20for%20skin%20colour%20because%20it's%20such%20a%20controversial%20and%20ethically%20fraught%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20Rollet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%20Bacciarelli%2C%20technology%20manager%20at%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20(HRW)%2C%20told%20VOA%20that%20Dahua%20technology%20should%20not%20contain%20skin%20tone%20analytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20companies%20have%20a%20responsibility%20to%20respect%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20prevent%20or%20mitigate%20any%20human%20rights%20risks%20that%20may%20arise%20as%20a%20result%20of%20their%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSurveillance%20software%20with%20skin%20tone%20analytics%20poses%20a%20significant%20risk%20to%20the%20right%20to%20equality%20and%20non-discrimination%2C%20by%20allowing%20camera%20owners%20and%20operators%20to%20racially%20profile%20people%20at%20scale%20%E2%80%94%20likely%20without%20their%20knowledge%2C%20infringing%20privacy%20rights%20%E2%80%94%20and%20should%20simply%20not%20be%20created%20or%20sold%20in%20the%20first%20place%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDahua%20denied%20that%20its%20surveillance%20products%20are%20designed%20to%20enable%20racial%20identification.%20On%20the%20website%20of%20its%20US%20company%2C%20Dahua%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BContrary%20to%20allegations%20that%20have%20been%20made%20by%20certain%20media%20outlets%2C%20Dahua%20Technology%20has%20not%20and%20never%20will%20develop%20solutions%20targeting%20any%20specific%20ethnic%20group.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Federal%20Communications%20Commission%20determined%20in%202022%20that%20the%20products%20of%20Chinese%20technology%20companies%20such%20as%20Dahua%20and%20Hikvision%2C%20which%20has%20close%20ties%20to%20Beijing%2C%20posed%20a%20threat%20to%20US%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2014%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20passed%20a%20revision%20proposal%20to%20its%20draft%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Law%2C%20a%20precursor%20to%20completely%20banning%20the%20use%20of%20facial%20recognition%20systems%20in%20public%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20facial%20recognition%20for%20mass%20surveillance%20from%20China%3B%20this%20technology%20has%20no%20place%20in%20a%20liberal%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Svenja%20Hahn%2C%20a%20German%20member%20of%20the%20European%20Parliament%20and%20Renew%20Europe%20Group%2C%20told%20Politico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20has%20long%20prohibited%20sectors%20such%20as%20healthcare%20and%20banking%20from%20discriminating%20against%20customers%20based%20on%20race.%20IBM%2C%20Google%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20restricted%20the%20provision%20of%20facial%20recognition%20services%20to%20law%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERollet%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20camera%20is%20filming%20at%20night%20or%20if%20there%20are%20shadows%2C%20it%20can%20misclassify%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaitlin%20Chin%20is%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20a%20Washington%20think%20tank%20where%20she%20researches%20technology%20regulation%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20this%20is%20something%20that's%20both%20very%20dehumanizing%20but%20also%20very%20concerning%20from%20a%20human%20rights%20perspective%2C%20in%20part%20because%20if%20there%20are%20any%20errors%20in%20this%20technology%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20false%20arrests%2C%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20discrimination%2C%20but%20also%20because%20the%20ability%20to%20sort%20people%20by%20skin%20colour%20on%20its%20own%20almost%20inevitably%20leads%20to%20people%20being%20discriminated%20against%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20VOA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691824020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-08%2Fcctv-generic_650x400_81471010632.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-surveillance-cams-that-can-detect-skin-color-raise-rights-concerns-4291706%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%20surveillance%20equipment%20maker%20Dahua%20is%20selling%20cameras%20with%20what%20it%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bskin%20colour%20analytics%26quot%3B%20feature%20in%20Europe%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20IPVM%2C%20as%20cited%20by%20Voice%20of%20America.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-surveillance-cams-that-can-detect-skin-color-raise-rights-concerns-4291706%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Modi's%20Boundaries%20And%20Sixers%20At%20Opposition's%20Expense%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20rare%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20in%20which%20the%20mover%20of%20the%20motion%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20walked%20out%20with%20its%20allies%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20response%20to%20the%20three-day%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverybody%20knew%20numbers%20were%20never%20the%20issue.%20However%2C%20a%20motion%20defeated%20by%20a%20voice%20vote%2C%20with%20no%20one%20in%20the%20opposition%20ranks%20to%20ask%20for%20an%20actual%20vote%2C%20was%20another%20rarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Modi%20government's%20stability%20was%20never%20in%20question%2C%20the%20only%20issue%20was%20who%20-%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20or%20the%2026-party%20INDIA%20born%20out%20of%20demise%20of%20UPA%20-%20uses%20this%20occasion%20best%20to%20its%20advantage.%20Which%20coalition%20effectively%20rips%20apart%20allegations%20from%20their%20rivals%2C%20constructs%20a%20compelling%20narrative%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20people%20and%20nation%20building%2C%20and%20provides%20substantial%20talking%20points%20that%20extend%20beyond%20rhetoric%20and%20gives%20political%20workers%2C%20supporters%20and%20sympathisers%20a%20message%20to%20take%20to%20the%20people%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reinstatement%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20membership%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20July%207%2C%20just%20a%20day%20before%20the%20debate%20on%20his%20party%20sponsored%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20had%20enthused%20secularists%20and%20left-liberals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wider%20world%2C%20there%20was%20much%20anticipation%2C%20though%20for%20a%20different%20reason.%20It%20was%20a%20given%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20speech%20and%20PM%20Modi's%20reply%20were%20going%20to%20be%20most-watched.%20The%20Congress's%20support%20system%20was%20at%20fever%20pitch%2C%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20the%20tiger%20will%20roar%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20stated%20objective%20of%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20by%20the%20opposition%20was%20Manipur%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20intervention%20too%20was%20closely%20watched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(a%20party%20neither%20aligned%20to%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20nor%20the%20opposition%20INDIA)%20MP%20Pinaki%20Mishra%20said%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20debate%20was%20noteworthy%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20believed%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20adept%20at%20snatching%20defeat%20from%20the%20jaws%20of%20victory.%20They%20are%20also%20very%20adept%20at%20cutting%20off%20their%20nose%20to%20spite%20their%20face.%20They%20know%20that%20every%20time%20the%20PM%20has%20got%20up%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20this%20House%2C%20he%20has%20pushed%20the%20Congress%20party%20through%20the%20shredder...%20This%20defies%20common%20sense%2C%20logic%2C%20political%20sense...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20flinging%20varied%20accusations%20at%20the%20government%2C%20including%20that%20PM%20Modi%20started%20speaking%20on%20Manipur%20only%20an%20hour%20into%20his%20speech.%20They%20also%20claim%20that%20Modi%20appeared%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bnervous%20and%20panicked%26quot%3B.%20Those%20who%20watched%20the%20proceedings%20can%20easily%20judge%20such%20claims%20on%20merits.%20The%20opposition%20came%20least%20prepared%20for%20the%20debate.%20The%20Congress's%20strategy%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20more%20cohesive%20and%20surcharged%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill%20debate%2C%20in%20support%20of%20their%20newfound%20ally%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20sound%20and%20fury%20was%20misdirected.%20Saying%20that%20he%20began%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20with%20%26quot%3Bahankar%26quot%3B%20(arrogance)%20and%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BBhedia%26quot%3B%20(jackal)%20who%20turned%20into%20a%20%26quot%3BChinti%26quot%3B%20(ant)%20was%20inevitably%20fodder%20for%20his%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabeling%20Modi%20as%20Ravan%2C%20once%20again%20dragging%20Adani%20into%20the%20debate%2C%20using%20words%20(not%20mentioning%20because%20expunged%20from%20proceedings)%20on%20Bharat%20Mata%20and%20a%20flying%20kiss%20while%20exiting%20the%20House%20redirected%20the%20Congress's%20focus%20toward%20damage%20control%20rather%20than%20amplifying%20what%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20provided%20enough%20ammo%20to%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20launch%20an%20attack%20on%20him%2C%20his%20party%20and%20his%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-no-trust-vote-plays-in-pm-modis-favour-4248719%5C%22%3EWhen%20Modi%20took%20the%20floor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20picked%20up%20right%20where%20he%20had%20left%20off%20during%20the%20no%20confidence%20debate%20in%20July%202018%20and%20the%20concluding%20session%20of%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20early%202019.%20He%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20the%20opposition%20for%20proving%20his%20five-year-old%20prophesy%20right%20and%20giving%20him%20the%20opportunity%20to%20speak%20on%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20on%20this%20platform%2C%20an%20opportunity%20he%20wouldn't%20have%20got%20otherwise.%20If%20that%20wasn't%20enough%2C%20he%20urged%20them%20to%20prepare%20better%20for%20a%20no%20confidence%20motion%20in%202028%2C%20implying%20that%20he%20would%20be%20in%20the%20closing%20months%20of%20his%20third%20term%20then.%20The%20sarcasm%20was%20unmissable%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20he%20was%20served%20this%20opportunity%20on%20a%20platter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20used%20words%2C%20phrases%2C%20and%20easy%20sentences%20in%20his%20characteristic%20style%2C%20which%20resonates%20with%20the%20hinterland.%20He%20made%20his%20audience%20laugh%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20his%20rivals%2C%20prompted%20them%20to%20reflect%20on%20the%20achievements%20of%20his%20government%20and%20the%20follies%20of%20his%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20down%20hard%20on%20appeasement%2C%20dynastic%20politics%20and%20the%20corrupt%20practices%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20calling%20it%20the%20GHAMANDIA%20(arrogant)%20alliance%20of%20parties%20who%2C%20in%20their%20attempt%20to%20use%20the%20country's%20name%2C%20%26quot%3Bonly%20ended%20up%20breaking%20it%20by%20putting%20dots%20after%20each%20letter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20describe%20how%20every%20opposition%20attack%20-%20like%20the%20no-trust%20move%20-%20was%20actually%20lucky%20for%20him%20and%20how%20his%20number%20increased%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20He%20predicted%20even%20better%20numbers%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM's%20statement%20also%20tackled%20criticism%20over%20the%20economy%2C%20from%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20in%20particular.%20Where%20they%20predicted%20the%20doom%20of%20the%20Indian%20banking%20sector%2C%20it%20fared%20better%20than%20western%20nations%2C%20which%20faced%20a%20banking%20crisis.%20Where%20they%20predicted%20doom%20for%20HAL%20(Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited)%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20it%20thrived.%20They%20predicted%20doom%20for%20the%20Life%20Insurance%20Corporation%20(LIC)%20after%20the%20Hindenburg-Adani%20controversy%20erupted%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20state-run%20insurer%20continues%20to%20flourish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20his%20lead-up%20to%20his%20%26quot%3Bguarantee%26quot%3B%2C%20of%20elevating%20India%20to%20the%20status%20of%20third%20largest%20economy%20after%20US%20and%20China%2C%20in%20his%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20started%20late%20on%20Manipur%2C%20over%20an%20hour%20into%20his%20reply%2C%20he%20stayed%20on%20the%20subject%20for%20about%2020%20minutes.%20The%20complexities%20he%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20outlined%20were%20not%20known%20to%20the%20world%20and%20neither%20were%20the%20historicity%20and%20the%20roots%20of%20the%20ethnic%20clashes.%20Modi%20didn't%20spare%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20ripping%20into%20their%20policies%20for%20the%20North-East%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru's%20All%20India%20Radio%20broadcast%20message%20to%20Assam%20throwing%20people%20in%20panic%20mode%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%20sending%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20fighter%20jets%20to%20bomb%20our%20own%20people%20in%20Manipur%20in%20March%201966%20were%20practically%20erased%20from%20public%20memory.%20So%20was%20Indira%20Gandhi%20handing%20over%20Katchatheevu%20island%20in%201974%20under%20a%20Indo-Sri%20Lanka%20maritime%20agreement.%20Now%20DMK%20chief%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20written%20to%20PM%20Modi%20to%20engage%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20get%20the%20island%20back%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress-led%20opposition%2C%20in%20its%20own%20wisdom%2C%20laid%20the%20pitch%20and%20bowled%20loose%20balls%20to%20allow%20Modi%20to%20hit%20fours%20and%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691823300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F9kbph7qo_pm-modi-lok-sabha-ani-650_650x400_10_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodis-boundaries-and-sixers-at-oppositions-expense-4291980%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20a%20rare%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20in%20which%20the%20mover%20of%20the%20motion%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20walked%20out%20with%20its%20allies%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20response%20to%20the%20three-day%20debate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodis-boundaries-and-sixers-at-oppositions-expense-4291980%22%2C%22c