0be%20managed%20by%20my%20and%20Zuck%E2%80%99s%20foundations%20(not%20UFC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELivestream%20will%20be%20on%20this%20platform%20and%20Meta.%20Everything%20in%20camera%20frame%20will%20be%20ancient%20Rome%2C%20so%20nothing%20modern%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20spoke%20to%20the%20PM%20of%20Italy%20and%20Minister%20of%20Culture.%20They%20have%20agreed%20on%20an%20epic%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1689963696703848449%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk%20vs.%20Zuckerberg%20for%20charity%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangiuliano%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20millions%20of%20euros%E2%80%9D%20are%C2%A0expected%20to%20be%20donated%20to%20two%20Italian%20pediatric%20hospitals%2C%20and%20scientific%20research%20for%20fighting%20childhood%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20culture%20minister%20again%20seemed%20to%20diverge%20from%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20interpretation%20of%20what%20was%20agreed%20upon%2C%20as%20the%20Tesla%20billionaire%20said%20on%20X%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20proceeds%20will%20go%20to%20veterans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20politician%20Carlo%20Calenda%2C%20a%20former%20industry%20minister%20and%20head%20of%20the%20centrist%20Azione%20party%2C%20criticized%20the%20culture%20minister%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20entertain%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20Musk%20vs%20Zuckerberg%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20find%20it%20simply%20mind-boggling%20that%20the%20Italian%20cultural%20heritage%20is%20being%20made%20available%20to%20two%20billionaires%20who%20want%20to%20indulge%20themselves%20like%20foolish%20teenagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2020%20this%20year%2C%20Musk%20asked%20on%20then-Twitter%20if%20Zuckerberg%2C%20who%20is%20trained%20in%20jiu