0Ukraine%20will%20continue%20to%20unfold%2C%20the%20war%20could%20drag%20on%20without%20a%20cease-fire%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-counteroffensive-more-or-less-double-fatalities-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691822094000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d70ea21f51cc0019684686%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-counteroffensive-more-or-less-double-fatalities-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chairman%20of%20the%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%20estimated%20in%20February%20that%20Ukraine%20had%20lost%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20soldiers%20since%20the%20war%20began%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A81%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-counteroffensive-more-or-less-double-fatalities-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Regresses%20to%20a%20Full-Blown%20Praetorian%20State%20as%20Curtains%20Draw%20on%20National%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F12115832%2Fshehbaz-sharif.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%209%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%2015%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpakistan-court-imran-khan-appeal-sharif-islamabad-5f99f8cebf2e300363bbfb47089d97ee%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Assembly%20(NA)%20was%20dissolved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20president%20upon%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20advice.%20The%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%20coalition%20federal%20government%2C%20which%20Sharif%20sat%20atop%20for%20the%20past%2016%20months%2C%20comprised%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20%E2%80%93%20eponymous%20with%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20elder%20brother%20and%20ex-PM%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20the%20religio-political%20Jamiat-e-Ulama-e-Islam%20(JUI)%20along%20with%20assorted%20smaller%20parties%2C%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%2C%20also%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20outgoing%20PM%20and%20the%20opposition%20leader%20in%20the%20NA%20have%2072%20hours%20to%20agree%20upon%20a%20nominee%20to%20lead%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20oversee%20the%20fresh%20general%20elections%2C%20which%20should%20be%20held%20within%2060%20days%20if%20the%20NA%20were%20dissolved%20after%20completing%20its%20full%20term.%20But%20in%20a%20tactical%20move%2C%20the%20outgoing%20coalition%20agreed%20to%20dissolve%20the%20NA%20three%20days%20before%20its%20end%20date%20of%20August%2012%2C%20thereby%20extending%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20new%20polls%20by%20an%20additional%2030%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20it.%20Just%20last%20week%2C%20the%20coalition%20government%20chose%20to%20certify%20new%20census%20results%2C%20which%20it%20had%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-digital-census%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esitting%20on%20since%20May%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20triggered%20a%20constitutional%20requirement%20to%20hold%20the%20next%20elections%20according%20to%20the%20new%20population%20data%2C%20which%20entails%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20that%20would%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpakistans-general-elections-under-new-census-indicates-delay-2023-08-05%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edelay%20the%20polls%20by%20several%20months%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20new%20elections%2C%20therefore%2C%20are%20highly%20unlikely%20to%20be%20held%20this%20year.%20In%20fact%2C%20yet%20another%20move%20by%20the%20outgoing%20dispensation%20to%20give%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexplainer-pakistan-has-just-given-more-powers-to-its-caretaker-government-and-it-is-not-good-news%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eextraordinary%20powers%20to%20the%20caretaker%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20beyond%20their%20usual%20remit%20of%20conducting%20polls%2C%20has%20led%20to%20speculation%20about%20whether%20elections%20would%20be%20held%20at%20all%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20There%20already%20are%20caretaker%20governments%20in%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Khyber-Pakhtunkhwa%20(KP)%20provinces%20which%20have%20been%20functioning%20unconstitutionally%20for%20several%20months.%20The%20Senate%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20is%20a%20permanent%20body%20elected%20indirectly%20through%20the%20provincial%20assemblies%2C%20has%20half%20its%20members%20retiring%20in%20March%202024.%20In%20principle%2C%20this%20sets%20a%20hard%20deadline%20at%20least%20for%20the%20provincial%20legislatures%20to%20be%20reelected%20by%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20why%20does%20the%20PDM%20not%20want%20to%20face%20the%20electorate%3F%20Why%20go%20through%20such%20convoluted%20and%20controversial%20manoeuvres%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20the%20spectre%20of%20former%20PM%20Imran%20Khan%20returning%20to%20power.%20And%20in%20this%2C%20the%20PDM%20is%20joined%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20all-powerful%20military%20and%2C%20especially%2C%20the%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20(COAS)%20General%20Asim%20Munir%20%E2%80%93%20against%20whom%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20once%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20favourite%2C%20has%20a%20personal%20vendetta.%20After%20having%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpakistan-elections-imran-khan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einstalled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20into%20power%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fin-pakistan-the-junta-hangs-on-to-its-imran-khan-project%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esustained%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20then%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fin-dumping-imran-khan-pakistan-army-seeks-face-saving-not-course-correction%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edumped%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20army%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fas-imran-loses-trust-vote-shehbaz-sharif-emerges-frontrunner-for-pak-pms-post%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eousted%20in%20a%20vote%20of%20no-confidence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20year.%20While%20the%20eventual%20trigger%20for%20the%20rancorous%20divorce%20was%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-trouble-in-hybrid-regimes-paradise-over-appointment-of-isi-chief%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eretaining%20his%20crony%20General%20Faiz%20Hameed%20Chaudhry%20as%20the%20ISI%20chief%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20curtains%20were%20called%20when%20the%20brass%20realised%2C%20belatedly%2C%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-armys-imran-khan-project-is-going-belly-up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20had%20been%20an%20unmitigated%20disaster%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adb.org%2Fcountries%2Fpakistan%2Feconomy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeconomy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transparency.org%2Fen%2Fcpi%2F2020%2Findex%2Fpak%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egovernance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20both%20his%20and%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20had%20hit%20rock-bottom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20so-called%20hybrid%20regime%20ended%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20tried%20to%20coax%20and%20cajole%20the%20then%20COAS%20and%20his%20one-time%20benefactor%20General%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa%20to%20regain%20power%20without%20making%20any%20headway.%20He%20then%20tried%20but%20failed%20to%20stonewall%20General%20Munir%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20as%20the%20COAS.%20Imran%20Khan%20weaved%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2022%2F04%2F01%2F1090192877%2Fpakistan-prime-minister-imran-khan-accuses-the-u-s-of-trying-to-oust-him%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efanciful%20theory%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20still%20remains%20popular%20with%20his%20followers%2C%20that%20the%20US%20sought%20his%20ouster%20and%20had%20commissioned%20the%20generals%20to%20do%20the%20hatchet%20job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20army%20proclaimed%20publicly%20that%20it%20had%20decided%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-army-vowed-to-remain-apolitical-in-a-presser-but-can-it-be-trusted%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eremain%20apolitical%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20but%20everyone%20saw%20it%20for%20the%20hogwash%20it%20was.%20Imran%20Khan%20trained%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20generals%2C%20not%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20correct%20the%20perennially%20lopsided%20civil-military%20balance%2C%20but%20to%20force%20them%20to%20intervene%20on%20his%20behalf.%20Failing%20that%2C%20the%20former%20cricketer-turned-demagogue%20shrewdly%20painted%20the%20PDM%20as%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20lapdog.%20He%20battered%20the%20coalition%20government%20for%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-07-01%2Fpakistan-inflation-accelerates-to-21-32-in-june-on-costly-oil%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espiralling%20inflation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20especially%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1700199%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efood%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F05%2F27%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fpakistan-fuel-price-crisis.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eoil%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0prices%2C%20and%20a%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgandhara.rferl.org%2Fa%2Fpakistan-rupee-record-low-inflation%2F31950578.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erupee%20plunging%20against%20the%20US%20dollar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20eroding%20the%20purchasing%20power%20of%20the%20people.%20Imran%20Khan%20deployed%20a%20straightforward%20populist%20strategy%20to%20boycott%20and%20discredit%20the%20parliament%2C%20mobilise%20the%20street%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%20social%20and%20traditional%20media%2C%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20a%20political%20martyr%20who%20had%20succumbed%20to%20a%20foreign%20intrigue%20carried%20out%20by%20domestic%20collaborators.%20His%20Pakistan%20Tehrik-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20scored%20several%20victories%20in%20by-elections%20across%20the%20country%2C%20which%20he%20turned%20into%20a%20referendum%20of%20sorts%20against%20the%20PDM%20and%20the%20generals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F10141826%2FScreenshot-2023-05-10-at-2.17.56-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F10141826%2FScreenshot-2023-05-10-at-2.17.56-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F10141826%2FScreenshot-2023-05-10-at-2.17.56-PM-300x155.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F10141826%2FScreenshot-2023-05-10-at-2.17.56-PM-1024x528.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-652415%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22619%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImran%20Khan.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20Twitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20dithering%20over%20critical%20decisions%20%E2%80%93%20including%20a%20crucial%20deal%20with%20the%20IMF%20%E2%80%93%20to%20recover%2C%20reboot%20and%20reform%20the%20economy%2C%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20its%20central%20plank%2C%20the%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%20squandered%20the%20PML-N%E2%80%99s%20political%20capital.%20The%20junior%20coalition%20partners%2C%20like%20the%20PPP%20in%20its%20Sindh%20power%20base%2C%20remained%20somewhat%20insulated%20but%20not%20entirely%20unscathed.%20The%20PDM%20government%20appeared%20to%20be%20flailing%20helplessly%20and%2C%20terrified%20of%20elections%2C%20it%20held%20the%20army%20in%20an%20even%20tighter%20embrace.%20The%20brass%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20was%20concerned%20about%20Imran%20Khan%20seeking%20retribution%20against%20generals%2C%20especially%20the%20COAS%2C%20were%20he%20to%20return%20to%20power.%20To%20stop%20an%20ascendant%20Khan%2C%20the%20PDM-Army%20combine%20went%20into%20a%20hybrid-plus%20mode.%20The%20PDM%2C%20which%20had%20set%20out%20to%20undo%20the%20Imran-Bajwa%20hybrid%20regime%2C%20and%20the%20army%20that%20vowed%20to%20remain%20apolitical%2C%20converged%20into%20the%20hybrid%202.0%20dispensation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20he%20appeared%20formidable%2C%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20however%2C%20had%20made%20monumental%20blunders%20along%20the%20way.%20Strategic%20miscalculations%20and%20tactical%20missteps%20like%20dissolving%20his%20own%20governments%20in%20the%20Punjab%20and%20KP%20provinces%2C%20shunning%20the%20parliament%20in%20favour%20of%20street%20agitation%20which%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20muster%2C%20and%20spurning%20the%20PDM%20government%E2%80%99s%20overtures%20for%20rapprochement%20and%20fresh%20elections%2C%20were%20to%20haunt%20and%20frustrate%20him.%20He%20ratcheted%20up%20his%20rhetoric%20against%20the%20top%20brass%2C%20including%20the%20former%20and%20incumbent%20COAS%2C%20drawing%20a%20public%20rebuke%20from%20the%20ISPR.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20superior%20judiciary%20still%20protected%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20army%20establishment%2C%20which%20had%20been%20mollycoddling%20him%20for%20years%2C%20stopped%20shielding%20him%20and%20possibly%20nudged%20the%20lower%20courts%20to%20proceed%20against%20him%20in%20a%20multitude%20of%20pending%20cases.%20The%20PDM%20government%20piled%20on%20with%20more%20charges%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20terrorism%2C%20sending%20the%20number%20of%20court%20cases%20against%20Imran%20Khan%20to%20almost%20as%20high%20as%20his%20ODI%20wickets%20tally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20sheer%20desperation%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20went%20virtually%20rogue.%20Delusionally%20overconfident%20about%20his%20popular%20support%20and%20backed%20by%20elements%20within%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20jostle%20his%20way%20back%20to%20power.%20When%20Khan%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1751782%2Fimran-khan-arrested-from-ihc-court-deems-ex-pms-arrest-legal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeventually%20arrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1751790%2Fimran-arrest-what-is-the-al-qadir-trust-case%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egraft%20charges%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20May%209%2C%20small%20protests%20erupted%20across%20the%20country%2C%20several%20of%20which%20went%20violent.%20Protestors%20breached%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nation.com.pk%2F10-May-2023%2Fghq-attacked-lahore-corps-commander-house-set-on-fire-by-pti-protesters%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGeneral%20Headquarters%20(GHQ)%20perimeter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Rawalpindi%2C%20set%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-pti-imran-khan-protests-violence%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECorps%20Commander%20Lahore%E2%80%99s%20residence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.radio.gov.pk%2F15-05-2023%2Fburnt-building-of-radio-pakistan-peshawar-to-be-opened-for-public-today%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehistoric%20Radio%20Pakistan%20Peshawar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20fire%2C%20and%20rampaged%20military%20symbols%20and%20installations%20around%20the%20country.%20The%20protests%20fizzled%20out%20the%20same%20day%2C%20but%20the%20choice%20of%20venues%20and%20violence%20stunned%20everyone%2C%20including%20the%20brass%2C%20which%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20precipitate%20a%20coup.%20Imran%20Khan%20had%20calculated%20that%20with%20pockets%20of%20support%20within%20the%20army%2C%20judiciary%2C%20and%20general%20public%2C%20he%20could%20bring%20down%20the%20top%20brass%20and%20upstage%20the%20PDM%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F05%2F11%2F1175451726%2Fpakistan-supreme-court-imran-khan-release%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereleased%20upon%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Pakistan%20(SCP)%E2%80%99s%20orders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0a%20day%20after%20detention%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20had%20the%20temerity%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fmay%2F14%2Fimran-khan-arrest-pakistan-military%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eindict%20General%20Munir%20by%20name%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20his%20arrest%20and%20plunging%20the%20country%20into%20crisis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecKermani%2Fstatus%2F1657268407023071232%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKhan%20charged%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20doubted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20any%20sense%20%5Bleft%5D%20in%20the%20Army%20Chief%20right%20now%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20so%20petrified%20if%20I%20win%20the%20elections%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20denotify%20%5Bsic%5D%20him%E2%80%A6%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fff773270-7a48-4be3-8c87-88c9b247f4e3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%E2%80%99s%20dismantling%20the%20future%20of%20this%20country%20to%20protect%20himself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20die%20was%20cast%3A%20only%20one%20of%20the%20two%20would%20remain%20standing.%20But%20the%20riot%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20trigger%20a%20rebellion%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20populist%20revolution%20that%20Imran%20Khan%20sought.%20The%20gamble%20had%20backfired.%20The%20army%20started%20a%20ruthless%20crackdown%20against%20the%20PTI%2C%20but%20the%20PDM%20government%20served%20as%20the%20face%20of%20it.%20Thousands%20of%20PTI%20workers%20and%20nearly%20all%20of%20its%20key%20leaders%20were%20arrested%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20will%20be%20tried%20in%20the%20military%20courts.%20The%20government%20ministers%20openly%20discussed%20the%20prospects%20of%20banning%20the%20PTI%20and%20trying%20Imran%20Khan%20himself%20under%20the%20draconian%20Army%20Act%20and%20the%20colonial-era%20Official%20Secrets%20Act.%20But%20the%20army%20instead%20opted%20to%20put%20its%20erstwhile%20darling%2C%20the%20PTI%2C%20on%20the%20chopping%20block.%20Clearly%20under%20duress%20from%20the%20junta%2C%20scores%20of%20PTI%20leaders%20have%20defected%2C%20denounced%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20publicly%20apologised%20for%20the%20May%209%20events%2C%20and%20pledged%20loyalty%20to%20the%20army.%20Most%20of%20these%20leaders%20were%20then%20herded%20into%20one%20new%20party%20and%20a%20new%20faction%20carved%20out%20of%20the%20PTI%2C%20while%20some%20have%20ostensibly%20quit%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20then%20last%20week%2C%20a%20lower%20court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Faug%2F05%2Fformer-pakistan-prime-minister-imran-khan-jailed-for-three-years%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econvicted%20and%20sentenced%20Imran%20Khan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20prison%20for%203%20years%20for%20misappropriation%20of%20state%20gifts%20and%20misdeclaration%20of%20assets.%20He%20was%20swiftly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpolice-arrest-former-pm-imran-khan-after-court-gives-three-year-prison-sentence-2023-08-05%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20incarcerated%20in%20the%20notoriously%20shabby%20Attock%20prison.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20(ECP)%20then%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F8%2F8%2Fformer-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-barred-from-politics-for-5-years%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edisqualified%20and%20barred%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20politics%20for%205%20years%2C%20which%20could%20also%20result%20in%20him%20being%20prohibited%20from%20chairing%20his%20own%20party.%20Imran%20Khan%20has%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F09%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fimran-khan-appeal-prison-sentence.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eright%20of%20appeal(s)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20superior%20courts%2C%20but%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20convicted%20and%20arrested%20in%20other%20cases%2C%20as%20the%20stage%20is%20being%20set%20to%20keep%20him%20from%20leading%20even%20his%20rump%20party%20in%20an%20election%2C%20if%20one%20is%20held%20at%20all.%20But%20the%20army%20most%20likely%20is%20not%20done%20with%20him%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoup%20de%20gr%C3%A2ce%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20yet%20to%20come.%20What%20that%20might%20look%20like%20is%20hard%20to%20say%20as%20the%20junta%20seems%20to%20be%20weighing%20each%20option%20and%20the%20expected%20domestic%20and%20international%20response%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM-300x147.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F07221444%2FScreenshot-2023-06-07-at-10.13.10-PM-1024x500.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-657074%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPakistan%20Army%20chief%20General%20Asim%20Munir.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20YouTube%2FISPR%20Official%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20clear%20though%20is%20that%20the%20political%20class%20in%20Pakistan%20has%20learnt%20no%20lesson.%20Six%20years%20ago%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fpakistan-politics-idINKCN1G51MI%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENawaz%20Sharif%20stood%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20Imran%20Khan%20stands%20today%3A%20convicted%2C%20imprisoned%20and%20debarred%20from%20politics%20over%20fabricated%20charges%20by%20an%20army-judiciary%20combine%2C%20with%20which%20Imran%20Khan%20had%20made%20a%20common%20cause.%20Whether%20Imran%20Khan%20is%20actually%20guilty%20of%20wrongdoing%20has%20been%20rendered%20irrelevant%20by%20the%20PDM-army%20nexus%20dismembering%20his%20party%20through%20yet%20another%20dreadful%20exercise%20in%20political%20engineering.%20True%20that%20Imran%20Khan%20has%20only%20himself%20to%20blame%20for%20ditching%20parliament%20and%20dissing%20the%20dialogue%20with%20political%20opponents%2C%20but%20the%20PDM%20cannot%20be%20absolved%20of%20bending%20and%20flouting%20the%20law%20to%20ostensibly%20give%20him%20a%20taste%20of%20his%20own%20medicine.%20The%20PTI%20and%20the%20PDM%E2%80%99s%20stints%20were%20effectively%20a%20throwback%20to%20the%201990s%2C%20when%20the%20PML-N%20and%20the%20PPP%20took%20turns%20seeking%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20patronage%20to%20batter%2C%20bruise%20and%20bump%20each%20other%20out%20every%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20The%20only%20outcome%20of%20such%20hobnobbing%20%E2%80%93%20then%2C%20now%2C%20and%20ever%20%E2%80%93%20to%20subvert%20the%20constitution%20and%20undermine%20the%20parliament%2C%20is%20crippling%20an%20already%20measly%20democracy%20while%20strengthening%20the%20army%20behemoth.%20In%20this%2C%20the%20outgoing%20NA%20may%20rank%20perhaps%20the%20worst%20even%20by%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20atrocious%20democratic%20standards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20PTI%20ruled%20by%20proclaiming%20ordinances%20from%20the%20high%20horse%20of%20hybrid%20regime%2C%20the%20PDM%E2%80%99s%20hybrid%202.0%20plunged%20to%20new%20lows%20by%20passing%20laws%20and%20amending%20the%20existing%20ones%20through%20stealth%20and%20subterfuge%20at%20breakneck%20speed.%20And%20each%20piece%20of%20legislation%20steamrolled%20thus%20is%20more%20repugnant%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20letter%20of%20the%20constitution%20than%20the%20other.%20And%20it%20was%20all%20done%20merely%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2428508%2Fgovt-rushes-crucial-bills-as-term-nears-end%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20hours%20before%20the%20NA%20ended%20its%20term%2C%20as%20if%20someone%20was%20holding%20a%20gun%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20head.%20After%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20departure%20from%20the%20NA%2C%20there%20is%20no%20legitimate%20opposition%20left%20in%20the%20house.%20The%20ostensible%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20is%20a%20PTI%20defector%20who%20is%20reportedly%20going%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%20on%20a%20PML-N%20ticket.%20But%20despite%20that%2C%20in%20unholy%20haste%2C%20the%20government%20didn%E2%80%99t%20share%20some%20proposed%20Bills%20even%20with%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20forcing%20members%20to%20protest.%20A%20PML-N%20loyalist%20and%20former%20PM%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2430026%2Fabbasi-terms-current-na-worst-in-pakistans-history%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EShahid%20Khaqan%20Abbasi%20apologised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20people%20for%20this%20%E2%80%98shameful%E2%80%99%20NA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20amendments%20rammed%20through%20the%20parliament%20included%20changes%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1767984%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficial%20Secrets%20Act%2C%201923%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2428164%2Fbill-ratifies-army-role-in-national-development%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArmy%20Act%2C%201952%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20former%20law%20now%20gives%20sweeping%20powers%20to%20the%20military%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20ISI%2C%20to%20raid%20any%20premises%20and%20detain%20any%20citizen%2C%20even%20under%20the%20mere%20suspicion%20of%20them%20breaching%20the%20law%2C%20and%20authorises%20them%20to%20use%20force%20if%20resisted.%20All%20they%20need%20is%20a%20nominal%20warrant.%20In%20an%20eerily%20Orwellian%20manner%2C%20the%20law%20also%20empowers%20these%20agencies%20with%20dystopian%20definitions%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98document%E2%80%99%20to%20include%20unwritten%20and%20intangible%20materials%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99%20to%20include%20even%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eunintentionally%20interacting%20with%20a%20person%20or%20entity%20that%20these%20outfits%20might%20consider%20hostile%20to%20the%20country.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20changes%20may%20be%20directed%20at%20the%20military%20personnel%20who%20are%20already%20being%20acted%20against%20for%20acts%20of%20omission%20or%20commission%20on%20May%209%2C%20the%20thrust%20of%20the%20amendment%20is%20to%20give%20legal%20cover%20to%20the%20ISI%E2%80%99s%20dirty%20tactics%20against%20dissidents%20of%20all%20shades.%20In%20effect%2C%20it%20provides%20%E2%80%93%20under%20the%20veneer%20of%20a%20nominal%20search%20warrant%20%E2%80%93%20the%20military%20intelligence%20agencies%20with%20the%20same%20powers%20that%20were%20once%20exercised%20by%20the%20Nazi%20Schutzstaffel%20(SS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20amendments%20to%20the%20Army%20Act%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20formalise%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20not%20just%20domestic%20commercial%20and%20investment%20enterprises%20but%20also%20sovereign%20state-to-state%20ventures.%20The%20insertion%20reads%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPakistan%20Army%20may%2C%20upon%20direction%20or%20with%20the%20concurrence%20of%20relevant%20authorities%20of%20the%20appropriate%20government%20in%20the%20prescribed%20manner%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%20carry%20out%20activities%20related%20to%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20national%20development%20and%20advancement%20of%20national%20or%20strategic%20interest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ostensible%20national%20development%2C%20the%20national%20or%20strategic%20interest%2C%20and%20its%20advancement%2C%20however%2C%20have%20not%20been%20defined.%20The%20amendment%20also%20gives%20a%20retrospective%20legal%20cover%20to%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20commercial%20activities%20in%20the%20past.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20parliament%20also%20hastily%20approved%20the%20Board%20of%20Investment%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20authorising%20the%20Special%20Investment%20Facilitation%20Council%20(SIFC)%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20through%20an%20ordinance%20as%20the%20PDM%20government%20ran%20up%20the%20exit%20ramp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20and%20his%20ministers%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwhole%20government%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cone%20window%E2%80%9D%20operation%20to%20attract%20foreign%20investment%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20Gulf%20countries%2C%20it%20effectively%20is%20a%20hybrid%20civil-military%20body%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arabnews.pk%2Fnode%2F2325301%2Fpakistan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eformalising%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20yet%20another%20economic%20entity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20army%20chief%20will%20sit%20in%20the%20SFIC%20apex%20committee%2C%20along%20with%20the%20PM%2C%20while%20army%20officials%20will%20head%20its%20national%20coordination%2C%20implementation%20and%20executive%20levels.%20The%20hybrid%202.0%20regime%20is%20calling%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenews.com.pk%2Fprint%2F1094271-sifc-a-consequence-of-exceptional-trust-level-between-pm-army-chief%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESFIC%20a%20game%20changer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ewith%20a%20scale%20larger%20than%20the%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC).%20Whether%20the%20project%20attracts%20investments%20such%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fgulf-nations-poised-to-invest-billions-in-pakistan-as-it-seeks-infusion-of-foreign-currency-9dfbb2ad%3Fst%3Ds1ecge60y4kzjwd%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESaudis%20potentially%20buying%20out%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20shares%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20copper%20mine%20in%20Balochistan%20or%20stagnates%20like%20the%20CPEC%2C%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769036%2Fcpec-to-sifc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eup%20for%20debate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20preeminence%20in%20the%20project%20indicates%20more%20than%20just%20reassuring%20the%20jittery%20Arab%20investors%20of%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%20It%20indicates%20that%20the%20governance%20paradigm%20has%20undergone%20a%20tectonic%20shift%20over%20the%20term%20of%20the%20outgoing%20NA.%20Failure%20of%20the%20first%20hybrid%20regime%2C%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20botched%20putsch%2C%20and%20the%20meek%20and%20mediocre%20PDM-PPP%20regime%20have%20all%20collectively%20enabled%20the%20army%20under%20General%20Munir%20to%20make%20a%20power%20and%20governance%20grab%20not%20seen%20since%201958%20when%20General%20Ayub%20Khan%20imposed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20martial%20law.%20Pakistan%2C%20since%20then%2C%20has%20been%20a%20coup-prone%20state%2C%20which%20oscillates%20between%20direct%20army%20rule%20or%20an%20indirect%20one%20where%20the%20junta%20rules%20through%20controlled%20democracies.%20Eric%20Nordlinger%20noted%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FSoldiers_in_Politics.html%3Fid%3D1tAWAAAAIAAJ%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESoldiers%20in%20Politics%3A%20Military%20Coups%20and%20Governments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20frequent%20sequel%20to%20military%20coups%20and%20government%20is%20more%20of%20the%20same%E2%80%A6%20The%20aftermath%20of%20military%20intervention%20is%20military%20intervention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20PDM-PPP%20regime%20exits%20the%20stage%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20whether%20Pakistan%20would%20remain%20under%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20boot%20or%20not%2C%20but%20of%20what%20form%20that%20might%20be%20in.%20The%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%E2%80%99s%20abject%20abdication%20of%20the%20political%20and%20governance%20space%20to%20the%20army%20and%20enabling%20the%20junta%20constitutionally%20and%20legally%20to%20sit%20atop%20the%20economic%20commanding%20heights%20has%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20an%20Indonesian-style%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F24490795%3Fread-now%3D1%26seq%3D4%23page_scan_tab_contents%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDwifungsi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20function%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Dwifungsi%20expanded%20the%20role%20of%20armed%20forces%20from%20territorial%20defence%20to%20involvement%20in%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20political%2C%20economic%20and%20social%20order.%20Under%20the%20dictator%20Suharto%2C%20army%20officers%20not%20only%20held%20positions%20in%20government%20ministries%20and%20corporations%20but%20were%20also%20given%2020%25%20seats%20in%20the%20parliament.%20The%202018-2023%20hybrid%20experiment%20in%20Pakistan%20has%20afforded%20all%20but%20the%20nominal%20perch%20in%20the%20parliament%20to%20serving%20officers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20did%20not%20have%20to%20turn%20out%20this%20way%2C%20and%20certainly%20did%20not%20end%20in%20such%20ignominy%20for%20the%20PDM%20politicians.%20But%20this%20was%20a%20choice%20they%20made%20when%20signing%20the%20Faustian%20bargain%20with%20the%20army.%20They%20opted%20for%20political%20expediency%20over%20struggle%2C%20and%20hand-me-down%20diluted%20power%20over%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate.%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eet%20al%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20chose%20a%20military%20solution%20to%20a%20civilian%20problem%2C%20which%20inevitably%20brings%20the%20army%20out%20of%20the%20garrisons%20not%20push%20it%20back%20into%20the%20barracks.%20Khan%20indeed%20is%20a%20problem%20of%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20making%20but%20relying%20on%20the%20army%20to%20dismantle%20him%20ensured%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20continued%20involvement%20in%20political%20engineering%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20preeminence.%20Chasing%20the%20mirage%20of%20power%20instead%20of%20going%20for%20fresh%20elections%20a%20year-and-a-half%20ago%2C%20when%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20slogan%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EVote%20ko%20izzat%20do%3C%2Fem%3E%20(respect%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20vote)%E2%80%99%20carried%20weight%20and%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20chips%20were%20down%2C%20had%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20disgraceful%20flight%20from%20polls%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20buck%2C%20however%2C%20stops%20with%20Mian%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20as%20the%20PDM%20effectively%20ruled%20in%20his%20name.%20While%20he%20may%20be%20away%20and%20constrained%20by%20legal%2C%20family%20and%20clique%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20but%20ultimately%20it%20is%20his%20party%2C%20his%20vote%20bank%2C%20and%20above%20all%20his%20stance%20that%20took%20the%20ultimate%20hit.%20Imran%20Khan%20may%20have%20been%20knocked%20out%20but%20was%20it%20worth%20the%20price%20paid%20in%20political%20capital%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F27162247%2Fnawaz-sharif-pti_0_0_0_0.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22701%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F27162247%2Fnawaz-sharif-pti_0_0_0_0.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F27162247%2Fnawaz-sharif-pti_0_0_0_0-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-283531%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22467%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFormer%20prime%20minister%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20way%20the%2015%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20NA%20divested%20itself%20of%20its%20own%20powers%20and%20surrendered%20its%20constitutional%20domain%20to%20the%20army%20is%20surpassed%20only%20by%20the%201985%20party-less%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20NA%20under%20General%20Ziaul%20Haq.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20even%20that%20assembly%20took%20almost%20six%20months%20to%20pass%20the%20in