t%3Cp%3ERia%20Litzenberg%2C%20University%20of%20T%C3%BCbingen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bbody%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20prehistoric%20ivory%20figurine%20was%20recently%20discovered%20in%20Germany.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20head%20was%20found%20in%201999%2C%20and%20for%20years%2C%20archaeologists%20believed%20it%20to%20be%20a%20horse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20they're%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20animal%20it%20actually%20is.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20minuscule%2C%20ivory%20figurine%20being%20pieced%20together%20over%2020%20years%20has%20confounded%20scientists%2C%20who%20thought%20the%20carving%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcliff-paintings-in-the-amazon-depict-ancient-humans-killing-mastodons-2020-12%5C%22%3Ea%20horse%20this%20whole%20time.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20figurine's%20head%20was%20first%20found%20in%201999%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneanderthal-hashtag-artwork-found-2014-9%5C%22%3EHohle%20Fels%20cave%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20important%20archaeological%20site%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F300000-year-giant-hand-axes-ice-age-sediments-england-mystery-2023-7%5C%22%3Eice%20age%20artifacts%3C%2Fa%3E%20nestled%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-germany-relocation-american-move-disappointing-2023-6%5C%22%3EGermany%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Swabian%20Jura%20region%20%E2%80%94%20and%20dates%20back%2035%2C000%20years%20ago.%20As%20scientists%20collected%20various%20parts%20of%20the%201-inch%20tall%20carving%20over%20the%20years%2C%20they%20stuck%20to%20the%20horse%20theory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20archaeologists%20discovered%20their%20fifth%20piece%2C%20a%20body%20fragment%2C%20in%202022.%20Now%20they're%20debating%20what%20animal%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20represented%20by%20the%20ancient%20carving%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3C