by%20no%20means%20always%20easy%20to%20identify%20Ice%20Age%20depictions%20with%20certainty%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20are%20preserved%20in%20such%20fragmentary%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20Conard%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BIt%20therefore%20makes%20sense%20to%20look%20extra%20carefully%20for%20the%20missing%20parts%20of%20this%20animal%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20figurines%20are%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Prehistoric%20Museum%20in%20Blaubeuren%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farchaeologists-35000-german-figurine-cave-lion-bear-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691808580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3034f7d2e90001946e1af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farchaeologists-35000-german-figurine-cave-lion-bear-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Archaeologists%20have%20found%20a%20fifth%20piece%20of%20an%20ivory%20figurine%20from%20the%20Ice%20Age%2C%20and%20now%20they're%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20on%20earth%20it's%20supposed%20to%20be.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hgetahun%40insider.com%20(Hannah%20Getahun)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farchaeologists-35000-german-figurine-cave-lion-bear-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Does%20India%20Not%20Celebrate%20or%20Commemorate%20the%20Battles%20of%20Op%20Pawan%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11224451%2FD29U15XVYAESA1-.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20every%20year%2C%20we%20commemorate%20Operation%20Vijay%20which%20helped%20us%20secure%20the%20%3Cspan%3Emilitary%20victory%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20Kargil%20War.%20This%20time%20around%20too%2C%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20nation%20rejoiced%20with%20celebrations%20held%20in%20several%20cities%2C%20as%20they%20should%20be.%20Around%20550%20military%20personnel%20of%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ell%20ranks%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20for%20the%20nation%20in%20the%201999%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKargil%20Vijay%20Diwas%20is%20a%20significant%20occasion%20dedicated%20to%20honour%20the%20extraordinary%20bravery%20and%20valour%20of%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces.%20This%20year%20too%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20held%20two-day%20long%20celebrations%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20National%20War%20Memorial%20in%20Delhi%20on%20July%2025%20and%2026.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20official%20celebration%2C%20numerous%20events%2C%20by%20individuals%20and%20organisations%2C%20were%20held%20across%20the%20country%20to%20pay%20tributes%20to%20soldiers%20who%20had%20sacrificed%20their%20lives%20in%20safeguarding%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20celebrations%20and%20events%20to%20remember%20the%20heroic%20acts%20of%20our%20soldiers%20are%20indeed%20necessary%2C%20for%20a%20%3Cspan%3Enation%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20honour%20its%20brave%20soldiers%20can%20never%20be%20a%20great%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20catch%20here.%20Besides%20the%20Kargil%20Diwas%2C%20the%20month%20of%20July%20also%20has%20another%20national%20and%20military%20significance.%20On%20July%2029%2C%201987%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Ethen-Indian%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20signed%20the%20India-Sri%20Lanka%20Peace%20Accord%2C%20ordering%20Indian%20troops%20to%20protect%20Indian%20interests%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%20This%20was%20the%20start%20of%20Operation%20Pawan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Op%20Vijay%20(Kargil)%20lasted%20for%20three%20months%2C%20Op%20Pawan%20lasted%20three%20years%20and%20the%20Liberation%20of%20Tamil%20Tigers%20Elam%20(LTTE)%20was%20vanquished%20only%20in%202009.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%20527%20soldiers%20gallantly%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E1%2C363%20soldiers%20were%20wounded%20in%20Op%20Vijay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Op%20Pawan%2C%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20respective%20figures%20were%20around%201%2C670%20and%203%2C000.%20As%20can%20be%20noticed%2C%20the%20casualty%20figures%20from%20the%20operation%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20are%20three%20times%20that%20of%20the%20Kargil%20War.%20However%2C%20only%20one%20Param%20Vir%20Chakra%20was%20awarded%20in%20relation%20to%20battles%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egainst%20an%20enemy%20known%20to%20be%20the%20wiliest%2C%20suicide-committed%2C%20fighting%20in%20its%20own%20territory%20with%20full%20support%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11224857%2F1200px-Women_of_the_LTTE_1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11224857%2F1200px-Women_of_the_LTTE_1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11224857%2F1200px-Women_of_the_LTTE_1-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11224857%2F1200px-Women_of_the_LTTE_1-1024x677.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667717%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22793%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELTTE%20troopers.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FCC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20even%20a%20single%20wreath%20has%20been%20placed%20or%20tricolour%20waved%20in%20acknowledgement%20of%20those%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20fighting%20in%20a%20foreign%20land%2C%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%20It%20is%20a%20sad%20reality%20that%20India%20does%20not%20celebrate%20or%20commemorate%20the%20battles%20of%20Op%20Pawan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20veterans%20are%20not%20prepared%20to%20forget%20their%20comrades.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20sought%20and%20received%20permission%20from%20the%20government%20to%20pay%20tributes%20to%20their%20fellow%20soldiers%20at%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news9live.com%2Findia%2Fop-pawan-a-war-india-forgot-2232052%2Famp%5C%22%3Eapprovals%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20in%202021%2C%20they%20came%20with%20a%20set%20of%20riders%2C%20that%20there%20will%20only%20be%20a%20silent%20ceremony%2C%20no%20serving%20officer%20in%20uniform%20to%20be%20present%2C%20and%20a%20wreath%20to%20be%20laid%20only%20by%20a%20senior-most%20officer%20present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%2C%20on%20July%2029%2C%20a%20silent%20ceremony%20was%20held%20at%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial%20for%20the%20third%20in%20a%20row.%20A%20small%20gathering%20of%20veterans%20and%20families%20honoured%20the%20martyrs.%20No%20serving%20officer%2C%20no%20minister%20or%20other%20elected%20representative%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20for%20whom%201%2C200%20died%20%E2%80%93%20attended%20the%20commemoration%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMagnanimously%2C%20this%20time%20around%2C%20the%20government%20allowed%20four%20wreaths%20to%20be%20laid.%20The%20first%20was%20laid%20by%20Major%20General%20Bhalla%2C%20then%20GOC%2C%2054%20Infantry%20Division.%20The%20second%20by%20the%20only%20serving%20officer%20present%2C%20Captian%20Raai%20from%2016%20Sikh.%20The%20third%20was%20by%20Colonel%20Rakesh%20Sidhu%2C%2015%20Mechanised%20Infantry%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20veterans%20who%20organised%20the%20ceremony.%20The%20final%20wreath%20was%20laid%20by%20the%20wife%20of%20gallantry%20award%20winner%20late%20Lance%20Naik%20Rajbir%20Singh%2C%205%20Rajput%20Regiment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20painful%20to%20note%20a%20sustained%20pressure%20by%20veterans%20was%20required%20to%20hold%20a%20small%20commemoration%20event.%20It%20feels%20the%20government%20is%20ashamed%20of%20something%2C%20that%20it%20had%20to%20be%20requested%20for%2C%20to%20honour%20the%20heroic%20acts%20of%20our%20soldiers%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20fondly%20remember%20the%20young%20officer%20of%20the%205%20Rajputana%20Rifles%20with%20whom%20I%20played%20many%20an%20interesting%20game%20of%20squash%20in%20the%20Kanpur%20club.%20He%20died%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20blown%20to%20pieces.%20Another%20colleague%2C%20Major%20Anil%20Kaul%2C%2065%20Armoured%20Regiment%2C%20lost%20an%20arm%20and%20an%20eye.%20Thirty%20soldiers%20of%20the%2013%20Sikh%20Light%20Infantry%2C%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20in%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20at%20Jaffna%20University%2C%20discharging%20their%20duty%20to%20comply%20with%20orders%20to%20capture%20or%20kill%20Liberation%20of%20Tamil%20Tigers%20Elam%20(LTTE)%20chief%2C%20V.%20Prabhakaran.%20My%20brother%2C%20then%20Major%20Manoj%20Asthana%20(artillery)%2C%20provided%20unlimited%20helicopter%20support%20to%20the%20infantry%20%E2%80%93%20machine%20gun%20fire%2C%20reconnaissance%20for%20commanders%2C%20and%20casualty%20evacuation%20in%20the%20jungles%20of%20Vavunia.%20His%20co-pilot%2C%20Harry%20Kaura%2C%20took%20a%20bullet%20on%20his%20face%2C%20in%20another%20mission%20flown%20by%20Daman%20Sehgal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20armies%20honour%20the%20soldierly%20code%20of%20not%20leaving%20their%20comrades%20behind%2C%20whether%20living%20or%20dead.%20However%2C%20many%20who%20died%20for%20Indian%20interests%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20were%20never%20brought%20back.%20Even%20their%20remains%20have%20not%20been%20brought%20back%20till%20today.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Foperation-pawan-heroes-ask-for-a-day-of-commemoration%2Farticle65786394.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3ELate%20Major%20Michael%20Lewis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2012%20Jat%20lies%20in%20an%20unmarked%20grave%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%20There%20are%20more%20unmarked%20graves%20in%20Palay%20and%20Vavuniya.%20There%20is%20no%20dedicated%20memorial%20for%20the%20Indian%20Peace%20Keeping%20Forces%20(IPKF)%20brave%20hearts%20in%20India.%20Strangely%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Sri%20Lankans%20who%20set%20up%20a%20dedicated%20memorial%20to%20the%20IPKF%20in%202008%20%E2%80%93%20the%20IPKF%20Memorial%20in%20Colombo%20and%20the%2010%20Para%20Memorial%20in%20Palaly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVictory%20has%20many%20fathers%2C%20but%20defeat%20has%20none.%20But%20was%20Op%20Pawan%20a%20defeat%20or%20a%20failure%3F%20Even%20if%20India%20is%20so%20inclined%2C%20why%20does%20it%20insult%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20the%20soldiers%20it%20sent%20to%20war%20on%20a%20legitimate%20mission%3F%20This%20was%20not%20Ethan%20Hunt%E2%80%99s%20(played%20by%20Tom%20Cruise)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98this%20is%20your%20mission%2C%20should%20you%20choose%20to%20accept%20it%E2%80%99%20type%20of%20volunteer%20service.%20Had%20they%20refused%2C%20they%20were%20liable%20for%20all%20consequences%20of%20disobedience%20of%20the%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20then%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20again%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20a%20nation%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20honour%20its%20braves%20can%20never%20be%20a%20great%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Falok-asthana%5C%22%3ECol%20Alok%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EAsthana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20veteran.%C2%A0He%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Red%20Pill%20on%20India%20and%20Indian%20Army%202023%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EHe%20can%20be%20contacted%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%2