ve%20says%20he%20was%20fired%20by%20Salesforce%20after%20raising%20concerns%20about%20software%20said%20to%20process%20and%20organize%20customer%20data%20in%20milliseconds%3A%20'It%20was%20all%20a%20lie.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Salesforce%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cf07f320f1cf0019cb6163%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESalesforce%20logo%20sign%20seen%20at%20the%20Salesforce%20tower%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20New%20York.%3Cp%3ELindsey%20Nicholson%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202022%2C%20Salesforce%20unveiled%20software%20that%20processes%20and%20organize%20customer%20data%20in%C2%A0%26quot%3Breal-time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20a%20former%20company%20vice%20president%20says%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20all%20a%20lie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20Salesforce%20retaliated%20against%20him%20for%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20product%20claims.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ex-%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-18-difficult-months-at-salesforce-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalesforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20vice%20president%20is%20suing%20his%20former%20employer%2C%20claiming%20the%20company%20lied%20about%20its%20software%20capabilities%20and%20retaliated%20against%20him%20for%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20product%20claims%2C%20court%20documents%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarl%20Wirth%2C%20who%20was%20Salesforce's%20vice%20president%20of%20product%20management%20when%20he%20joined%20the%20company%20in%202020%20before%20being%20promoted%20to%20senior%20vice%20president%20in%20January%202022%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20filed%20on%20July%2028%20that%20the%20company%20falsely%20advertised%20the%20capability%20of%20its%20Customer%20Data%20Platform%20(CDP).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECDP%20is%20marketing-industry%20speak%20for%20software%20that%20can%20process%20and%20organize%20user%20data%20to%20create%20a%20unique%20customer%20profile%20which%20companies%20can%20then%20use%20to%20advertise%20a%20product%20or%20create%20a%20personalized%20customer%20experience.%20Salesforce%20promoted%20that%20its%20CDP%20can%20process%20large%20amounts%20of%20customer%20data%20in%20%26quot%3Breal-time%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20in%20%26quot%3Bmilliseconds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20benefit%20to%20real-time%20data%20processing%20that%20Salesforce%20advertises%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20when%20a%20hospital%20may%20need%20the%20most%20up-to-date%20information%20on%20a%20patient%20regarding%20urgent%20healthcare%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20milliseconds%20matter%20most%2C%20your%20healthcare%20provider%20can%20deliver%20proactive%20guidance%20and%20care%20recommendations%20with%20access%20to%20your%20real-time%20patient%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salesforce.com%2Fap%2Fblog%2F2022%2F09%2Fwhat-is-salesforce-genie.html%23genie-business-impact%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20company%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%20unveiled%20its%20CDP%20software%2C%20Genie%2C%20to%20the%20public%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-dreamforce-acquisitions-growth-margins-revenue-target-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%20keynote%20slide%20attached%20to%20the%20court%20documents%2C%20the%20company%20repeats%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Breal-time%26quot%3B%20four%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20court%20documents%2C%20Salesforce%20said%20it%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20announcement%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20made%20since%20the%20founders%20started%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20all%20a%20lie%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20documents%20say%20the%20software%20does%20not%20operate%20as%20fast%20as%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Breal-time%26quot%3B%20suggests%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bin%20fact%20many%20of%20its%20processes%20took%20several%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20was%20able%20to%20execute%20some%20functions%20such%20as%20information%20collection%20in%20real%20time%2C%20other%20operations%20such%20as%20the%20processing%20and%20organizing%20of%20that%20data%20took%20hours%20to%20complete%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salesforce.com%2Fap%2Fblog%2F2022%2F09%2Fwhat-is-salesforce-genie.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalesforce's%20website%20about%20Genie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20says%20the%20software%20%26quot%3Bcollects%20and%20unifies%20data%20in%20milliseconds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20personalized%20offer%20on%20a%20website%20you're%20browsing%20changes%20instantly%20because%20of%20something%20you%20just%20clicked%20in%20a%20marketing%20email%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20writes.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20company%20uses%20Marketing%20Cloud%20Genie%2C%20that%20offer%20changes%20immediately%20into%20something%20that%20is%20more%20relevant%20to%20you%20than%20the%20one%20you'd%20otherwise%20be%20looking%20at.%20This%20convinces%20you%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20make%20a%20purchase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWirth%20recommended%20that%20Salesforce%20pursue%20this%20software%20capability%20in%20late%202021%20or%20early%202022%2C%20according%20to%20court%20documents%2C%20but%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20the%20Customer%20Data%20Platform%20(CDP)%20team%20that%20it%20could%20not%20%26quot%3Bdevelop%20the%20technology%20in%20time%26quot%3B%20for%20Salesforce's%20announcement%20in%20September%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20CDP%20team%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20redefine%20the%20meaning%20of%20'real-time%2C'%20so%20that%20it%20could%20falsely%20claim%20that%20the%20CDP%20operated%20in%20real-time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiff%20reasonably%20believed%20that%20publicly%20claiming%20the%20CDP%20operated%20in%20'real-time'%20without%20actually%20having%20(or%20even%20intending%20to%20have%20in%20the%20near%20future)%20such%20a%20capability%20would%20be%20fraudulent%2C%20and%20likely%20violate%20numerous%20provisions%20of%20Federal%20law%20relating%20to%20fraud%20against%20shareholders%2C%20as%20well%20as%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWirth%20then%20decided%20to%20act%20as%20a%20whistleblower%20and%20brought%20up%20his%20concerns%20to%20the%20CDP%20team%20and%20other%20%26quot%3Bkey%20executives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20he%20approached%20his%20direct%20supervisor%2C%20Lidiane%20Jones%2C%20now%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-lidiane-jones-the-new-slack-ceo-succeeding-stewart-butterfield-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20of%20Slack%20Technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%20his%20concerns.%20The%20lawsuit%20says%20Jones%20then%20began%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeceitful%20campaign%20to%20diminish%26quot%3B%20Wirth's%20reputation%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Wirth's%20last%20%26quot%3Bwhistleblowing%20activities%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20one-on-one%20meeting%20with%20Saleseforce's%20CTO%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparker-harris-salesforce-cofounder-profile-2015-2%5C%22%20t