onicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66480636%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66480636.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66480636.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Special%3A%20Manipur%20Violence%20Broke%20Out%20Days%20Before%20MHA%20Was%20to%20Finalise%20Kuki%20Accord%20that%20CM%20Did%20Not%20Support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01100536%2FScreenshot-2023-06-01-at-10.05.28-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20was%20set%20to%20finalise%20a%20peace%20accord%20with%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20on%20May%208%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%2C%20but%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20Torbung%20area%20of%20the%20Churachandpur-Bishnupur%20border%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%20that%20spiralled%20into%20a%20cycle%20of%20violence%20which%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20controlled%2C%20put%20paid%20to%20those%20plans.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20MHA%20have%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20groups%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20were%20to%20be%20invited%20to%20visit%20New%20Delhi%20to%20formalise%20the%20accord%20as%20an%20outcome%20of%20the%20peace%20talks%20being%20carried%20on%20with%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20through%20an%20interlocutor%20since%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20some%20groups%20that%20have%20been%20under%20SoO%20since%202008.%20A%20leader%2C%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20corroborated%20the%20information%20shared%20by%20the%20MHA%20sources.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20we%20had%20almost%20reached%20an%20agreement%3B%20the%20modalities%20of%20that%20accord%20were%20to%20be%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20which%20has%20been%20our%20demand.%20We%20were%20given%20the%20impression%20that%20we%20will%20get%20an%20autonomous%20territorial%20council%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20like%20the%20Bodos%20of%20Assam%20have%2C%20which%20would%20have%20been%20a%20significant%20win%20for%20our%20political%20movement.%20With%20financial%20independence%20from%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Imphal%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20almost%20like%20having%20a%20separate%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0The%20insurgent%20leader%2C%C2%A0however%2C%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CPost%20May%203%20violence%20though%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20public%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20state%2C%20not%20territorial%20council%2C%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20our%20stand%20is%20also%20changing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiren%C2%A0Singh%20not%20in%20support%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20signing%20a%20peace%20treaty%20with%20the%20Kuki%20SoO%20groups%20on%20May%208%2C%20but%20the%20Manipur%20government%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20was%20not%20and%20he%20made%20that%20amply%20clear%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%20He%20%E2%80%9Chad%20got%20a%20wind%20of%20it%20and%20was%20extremely%20unhappy%3B%20he%20was%20sending%20us%20feelers%20through%20various%20channels%20not%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20sources%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Meitei%20civil%20society%C2%A0organisations%C2%A0(CSOs)%20have%20been%20opposed%20to%20bringing%20the%C2%A0Kuki-dominated%20areas%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20and%C2%A0thereby%C2%A0granting%C2%A0them%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20administration%E2%80%9D%20under%20an%20autonomous%C2%A0territorial%20council.%20They%20feared%20that%C2%A0granting%20a%20separate%20financial%20channel%20to%20them%20directly%20with%20Delhi%C2%A0would%C2%A0amount%20to%C2%A0affecting%C2%A0the%20%E2%80%9Cterritorial%20integrity%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Manipur%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20event%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20being%20able%20to%20formalise%20this%20deal%20with%20the%20Kukis%20on%20May%208%2C%20it%20would%20have%20had%20every%20likelihood%20of%20creating%20widespread%20disappointment%20within%20the%20Meitei%20groups%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20sparking%20protests.%20Sources%20say%20that%20Singh%20being%20on%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20chair%20and%20hailing%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20feared%20being%20left%20vulnerable%20directly%20to%20backlash%20from%20his%20%E2%80%98own%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20move%20directly%20affecting%20his%20political%20career.%20Singh%20has%20anyway%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2Fnortheast%2F2023%2Fapr%2F17%2Fdissidence-brews-against-cm-n-biren-singh-in-manipur-disgruntled-mlas-camping-in-delhi-2566808.html%5C%22%3Efacing%C2%A0protracted%C2%A0rebellion%20from%20within%20his%20party%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20by%20other%20Meitei%20leaders%C2%A0of%20the%20BJP.%20Batches%20of%20party%20MLAs%20have%20been%20visiting%20New%20Delhi%20till%20as%20late%20as%20this%20April%2C%20demanding%20a%20change%20in%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reached%20out%20to%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20for%20comments%3B%20but%20all%20of%20them%20refused%20to%20speak%2C%20citing%20no%20knowledge%20of%20the%20proposed%20peace%20accord%20with%20the%C2%A0Kuki%C2%A0SoO%20groups%C2%A0on%20May%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20a%20former%20colleague%20of%20Singh%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20said%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20likely%20proposal.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20led%20Union%20government%20must%20have%20been%20looking%20at%20securing%20the%20Manipur%20Outer%20parliamentary%20seat%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20by%20granting%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20to%20the%20Kukis%2C%20it%20would%20have%20directly%20affected%20Biren.%20It%20would%20have%20meant%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Meitei%20public%20that%20would%20have%20risen%20against%20him%20but%20the%20rebellion%20within%20his%20party%20to%20remove%20him%20would%20have%20only%20got%20stronger.%20So%20trying%20to%20stall%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20move%20would%20suit%20his%20political%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17200237%2FScreenshot-2023-05-17-at-8.02.32-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22942%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17200237%2FScreenshot-2023-05-17-at-8.02.32-PM.png%20942w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17200237%2FScreenshot-2023-05-17-at-8.02.32-PM-300x162.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-653506%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22510%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20from%20a%20video%20purportedly%20showing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20on%20the%20night%20of%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20MLA%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20then%20brings%20up%20serious%20questions%3A%20As%20Biren%20had%20insider%20information%20on%20the%20peace%20accord%3B%20did%20he%20try%20to%20turn%20the%20possible%20tide%20against%20him%20with%20help%20from%20radical%20groups%20like%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%20who%20are%20his%20supporters%3F%20Since%20those%20groups%20are%20being%20accused%20of%20unleashing%20violence%20on%20the%20Kukis%20in%20I