0of%205%20to%2018%20years%20are%20given%20shelter%20at%20child%20welfare%20homes%20till%20they%20are%20reunited%20with%20their%20families.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20these%20children%20are%20intellectually%20disabled.%20So%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20understand%20where%20they%20come%20from%20and%20who%20their%20parents%20are.%20This%20is%20when%20we%20seek%20help%20from%20psychologists%2C%20who%20assist%20them%20so%20that%20we%20can%20track%20their%20locations%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Himanshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20psychologists%20are%20able%20to%20get%20the%20required%20information%2C%20photos%20of%20children%20are%20circulated%20in%20the%20local%20police%20stations.%20After%20identifying%20the%20village%2C%20these%20children%20are%20reunited%20with%20their%20families%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-2-1691757624.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20IAS%20officer%20feels%20that%20this%20work%20is%20also%20part%20of%20his%20duty.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-2-1691757624.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-2-1691757624-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-2-1691757624-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-2-1691757624-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-2-1691757624-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327083%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20feels%20that%20this%20work%20is%20also%20part%20of%20his%20duty.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20impoverished%20families%20are%20unable%20to%20travel%20to%20Varanasi%2C%20departmental%20officials%20are%20deployed%20to%20accompany%20the%20child%20and%20safely%20take%20them%20to%20their%20homes.%20A%20%E2%80%9Chappy%E2%80%9D%20picture%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173394%2Findia-kumbh-mela-lost-children-rescue-help%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereunited%20families%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealong%20with%20officials%20is%20clicked%20to%20maintain%20record.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20we%20follow%20up%20on%20all%20cases.%20We%20regularly%20video%20or%20phone%20call%20the%20families%20to%20ensure%20children%20are%20safe.%20We%20talk%20to%20the%20children%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUntil%20reunited%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F138862%2Fface-recognition-software-helps-find-missing-children-in-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20are%20reunited%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20their%20families%2C%20they%20are%20housed%20in%2020%20child%20welfare%20shelters%20that%20have%20been%20equipped%20with%20improved%20facilities%20including%20air%20conditioning%20and%20smart%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTill%20the%20time%2C%20they%20are%20not%20reunited%2C%20they%20are%20like%20our%20children.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20good%20facilities%20available%20at%20the%20shelter%20homes.%20In%20the%20morning%20after%20Yoga%20classes%2C%20they%20get%20involved%20in%20different%20sports%20activities%20and%20are%20engaged%20in%20making%20crafts%20and%20paintings.%20Children%20are%20also%20given%20regular%20medical%20check-ups%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20h