agging-belarus-into-the-ukraine-war-12938008%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Govt%20Unveils%20Controversial%20New%20Criminal%20Bills%3A%20'Sedition'%20Law%20to%20Change%20But%20in%20Name%20Only%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09222428%2FAmit-Anil-Chandra-Shah-in-Lok-Sabha.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Friday%20(August%2011)%20announced%20in%20parliament%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Crepeal%E2%80%9D%20the%20sedition%20law%2C%20as%20he%20introduced%20three%20new%20Bills%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20a%20move%20to%20reform%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20and%20shed%20its%20colonial%20legacy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20new%20bills%20include%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%3B%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201898%3B%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20British%20laws%20were%20made%20to%20strengthen%20and%20protect%20the%20British%20government%20and%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20punish%20and%20not%20bring%20justice.%20The%20spirit%20of%20three%20new%20laws%20that%20we%20are%20bringing%20will%20not%20be%20to%20punish%20but%20to%20give%20justice%20to%20every%20citizen%20and%20to%20prevent%20further%20crimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20gave%20a%20brief%20introduction%20of%20the%20three%20new%20Bills%20and%20said%20that%20they%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20and%20will%20be%20presented%20to%20the%20parliament%20thereafter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposed%20legislation%20brings%20important%20changes%2C%20by%20criminalising%20mob%20lynching%20and%20marrying%20or%20having%20sexual%20relations%20with%20a%20woman%20by%20deception.%20It%20also%20provides%20for%20compulsory%20video%20recording%20of%20the%20statements%20by%20victims%20of%20sexual%20crimes%2C%20imposing%20time%20limits%20for%20filing%20chargesheets%20and%20completion%20of%20trials%2C%20as%20well%20as%20conducting%20trials%20for%20criminals%20who%20are%20absconding%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESedition%20replaced%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98draconian%E2%80%99%20provision%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20important%20change%2C%20however%2C%20as%20hailed%20by%20Shah%2C%20has%20been%20to%20drop%20the%20provision%20of%20sedition%20under%20Section%20124A%20of%20the%20IPC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSedition%20(law)%20was%20brought%20(by%20the%20British)%20to%20save%20their%20rule.%20We%20have%20taken%20the%20historic%20decision%20to%20repeal%20sedition%20completely.%20This%20is%20a%20democracy%2C%20everyone%20has%20the%20right%20to%20speak%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20look%20at%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2Fthe-bharatiya-nyaya-sanhita-2023-485731.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Section%20150%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%202023%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eshows%20that%20while%20the%20word%20sedition%20may%20have%20been%20removed%2C%20the%20law%20remains%20and%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20has%20been%20made%20more%20draconian%20by%20making%20it%20punishable%20with%20imprisonment%20for%20life%20or%20seven%20years%20imprisonment%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESection%20150%20details%20Acts%20endangering%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20unity%2C%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%2C%20purposely%20or%20knowingly%2C%20by%20words%2C%20either%20spoken%20or%20written%2C%20or%20by%20signs%2C%20or%20by%20visible%20representation%2C%20or%20by%20electronic%20communication%20or%20by%20use%20of%20financial%20mean%2C%20or%20otherwise%2C%20excites%20or%20attempts%20to%20excite%2C%20secession%20or%20armed%20rebellion%20or%20subversive%20activities%2C%20or%20encourages%20feelings%20of%20separatist%20activities%20or%20endangers%20sovereignty%20or%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%3B%20or%20indulges%20in%20or%20commits%20any%20such%20act%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20for%20life%20or%20with%20imprisonment%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20seven%20years%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20explanation%20of%20the%20section%20states%20the%20following%3A%20%E2%80%9CComments%20expressing%20disapprobation%20of%20the%20measures%2C%20or%20administrative%20or%20other%20action%20of%20the%20Government%20with%20a%20view%20to%20obtain%20their%20alteration%20by%20lawful%20means%20without%20exciting%20or%20attempting%20to%20excite%20the%20activities%20referred%20to%20in%20this%20section.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20Sedition%20law%20(Under%20124A%20IPC)%20had%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%20by%20words%2C%20either%20spoken%20or%20written%2C%20or%20by%20signs%2C%20or%20by%20visible%20representation%2C%20or%20otherwise%2C%20brings%20or%20attempts%20to%20bring%20into%20hatred%20or%20contempt%2C%20or%20excites%20or%20attempts%20to%20excite%20disaffection%20towards%2C%20the%20Government%20established%20by%20law%20in%203%5BIndia%5D%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%205%5Bimprisonment%20for%20life%5D%2C%20to%20which%20fine%20may%20be%20added%2C%20or%20with%20imprisonment%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20three%20years%2C%20to%20which%20fine%20may%20be%20added%2C%20or%20with%20fine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20explanation%2C%20the%20law%20defined%20the%20expression%20%E2%80%9Cdisaffection%E2%80%9D%20as%20including%20disloyalty%20and%20all%20feelings%20of%20enmity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Section%20also%20explained%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccomments%20expressing%20disapprobation%20of%20the%20measures%20of%20the%20Government%20with%20a%20view%20to%20obtain%20their%20alteration%20by%20lawful%20means%2C%20without%20exciting%20or%20attempting%20to%20excite%20hatred%2C%20contempt%20or%20disaffection%2C%20do%20not%20constitute%20an%20offence%20under%20this%20section.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20further%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccomments%20expressing%20disapprobation%20of%20the%20administrative%20or%20other%20action%20of%20the%20Government%20without%20exciting%20or%20attempting%20to%20excite%20hatred%2C%20contempt%20or%20disaffection%2C%20do%20not%20constitute%20an%20offence%20under%20this%20section.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EAnas%20Tanwir%2C%20advocate%20on%20record%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20founder%20of%20Indian%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20said%20that%20the%20explanation%20under%20Section%20150%20of%20the%20new%20law%20is%20%E2%80%9Cincomplete%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20removed%20sedition%2C%20it%20makes%20a%20far%20more%20draconian%20provision.%20The%20explanation%20of%20the%20law%20appears%20incomplete.%20And%20it%20brings%20into%20its%20purview%20the%20potential%20to%20criminalise%20protest%20against%20any%20law%20or%20any%20action%20that%20the%20govt%20does%20not%20deem%20fit%20by%20using%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98subversive%20activity%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20a%20very%20vague%20term%20and%20can%20include%20anything%2C%20even%20a%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20offences%20and%20stricter%20punishments%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20said%20that%20in%20recent%20years%20there%20has%20been%20talk%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20law%20for%20mob%20lynching%20which%20has%20been%20addressed%20in%20the%20new%20legislation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20has%20been%20said%20about%20mob%20lynching%20in%20the%20last%20seven%20years.%20Now%20mob%20lynching%20will%20have%20a%20punishment%20of%20seven%20years%20imprisonment%20or%20for%20life%20or%20death%20penalty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20added%20that%20in%20cases%20of%20gang%20rape%2C%20punishment%20has%20been%20increased%20and%20may%20now%20include%2020-year%20imprisonment%20as%20well%20as%20imprisonment%20for%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20involving%20girls%20less%20than%2018%20years%20old%2C%20provision%20of%20capital%20punishment%20has%20been%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20absconding%20criminals%20like%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%2C%20Shah%20said%20provisions%20have%20been%20made%20to%20hold%20trials%20in%20absentia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20cases%2C%20people%20like%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20would%20commit%20crimes%20and%20run%20away.%20Now%20trials%20will%20take%20place%20despite%20their%20absence.%20If%20they%20have%20to%20appeal%20against%20the%20judgment%2C%20then%20they%20have%20to%20come%20to%20India%20and%20then%20appeal%20to%20Indian%20courts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20cases%20of%20criminals%20who%20have%20political%20clout%20and%20remission%20of%20their%20sentences%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20be%20let%20go%E2%80%9D%20as%20was%20seen%20in%20Bihar%20recently%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-did-the-bihar-govt-change-remission-rules-to-aid-the-release-of-convicted-killer-anand-mohan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealluding%20to%20the%20release%20of%20Anand%20Mohan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20account%20of%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20heft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20sentence%20can%20be%20remitted%20from%20death%20to%20life%20imprisonment%2C%20life%20imprisonment%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20seven%20years%20to%20three%20years.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20political%20connections%20will%20not%20be%20let%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20a%20separate%20category%20of%20crime%20has%20been%20brought%20for%20marrying%20or%20having%20sexual%20relations%20with%20a%20woman%20by%20deception%20or%20wrong%20credentials%2C%20as%20well%20as%20snatching%20which%20was%20not%20defined%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20laws%20will%20also%20make%20it%20compulsory%20for%20the%20police%20to%20record%20video%20statements%20of%20a%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20abuse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20order%20to%20streamline%20the%20trial%20and%20chargesheeting%20process%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20a%20time%20limit%20of%2090%20days%20will%20be%20imposed%20within%20which%20a%20chargesheet%20has%20to%20be%20filed.%20This%20deadline%20can%20be%20extended%20by%20another%2090%20days%20by%20courts%20but%20after%20180%20days%20the%20case%20will%20have%20to%20go%20to%20trial.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20arguments%20conclude%2C%20judgments%20have%20to%20be%20given%20by%20courts%20within%2030%20days.%20Judgments%20will%20also%20have%20to%20be%20uploaded%20within%20seven%20days%20so%20an%20appeal%20can%20be%20filed%20if%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOrganised%20crime%20has%20also%20been%20made%20a%20punishable%20offence%20and%20community%20service%20has%20been%20introduced%20for%20the%20first%20time%20for%20certain%20crimes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20order%20to%20bring%20accountability%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20force%20will%20have%20to%20provide%20documentary%20and%20digital%20evidence%20if%20a%20person%20has%20been%20arrested.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COften%20we%20see%20that%20the%20police%20after%20arresting%20a%20person%20don%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything%20for%20up%20to%204%20days.%20Now%20they%20will%20have%20to%20give%20physical%20and%20digital%20notification%20to%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20accused%20that%20their%20kin%20has%20been%20taken%20into%20custody.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20changes%20have%20been%20brought%20in%20to%20digitise%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system.%20Forensic%20evidence%20has%20been%20mandatory%20for%20crimes%20punishable%20with%207%20years%20and%20above.%20If%20a%20case%20that%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20over%207%20years%20has%20to%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20then%20it%20has%20to%20take%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20consent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20protect%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKey%20features%20of%20new%20Bills%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20said%20that%20the%20three%20new%20Bills%20will%20bring%20important%20changes%20to%20make%20them%20relevant%20to%20Indian%20society%20and%20drop%20references%20to%20colonial%20rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20which%20will%20replace%20CrPC%20will%20have%20533%20provisions.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20changed%20160%20provisions%2C%20added%209%20new%20provisions%20and%209%20provisions%20have%20been%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20IPC%20will%20have%20511%20provisions%20against%20the%20356%20in%20the%20earlier%20law.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20changes%20in%20175%20provisions%2C%208%20new%20provisions%20have%20been%20added%20and%2022%20have%20been%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20will%20have%20170%20provisions%20instead%20of%20the%20166%20earlier.%20%E2%80%9C23%20provisions%20have%20been%20changed%2C%20one%20has%20been%20added%20and%20five%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Shah%2C%20these%20three%20laws%20were%20full%20of%20references%20to%20colonialism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20existing%20laws%20have%20references%20to%20the%20parliament%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20provincial%20act%2C%20notification%20by%20the%20Crown%2C%20London%20Gazette%2C%20jury%20and%20Barrister(which%20is%20not%20there%20in%20our%20country)%2C%20Lahore%20government%2C%20Commonwealth%2C%20Privy%20Council%2C%20British%20Crown%2C%20Court%20of%20Justice%20in%20England%2C%20Her%20Majesty%20dominions%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%20475%20references%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egulaami%20ki%20nishani%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(signs%20of%20slavery)%20have%20been%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EManner%20of%20introduction%20%E2%80%98unfair%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20new%20legislations%20will%20overhaul%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%2C%20lawyers%20said%20that%20it%20could%20bring%20operational%20difficulties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20were%20also%20raised%20that%20the%20Bills%20were%20introduced%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20and%20listed%20moments%20before%20their%20introduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20have%20been%20a%20wider%20consultation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tanwir.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIntroduction%20on%20the%20last%20day%20is%20unfair%20but%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20may%20consider%20amending%20rather%20than%20bringing%20new%20laws%20as%20there%20may%20be%20difficulties%20in%20interpreting%20provisions%2C%20bringing%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%20that%20the%20move%20to%20bring%20in%20changes%20like%20defining%20mob%20lynching%20is%20welcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20welcome%20move%20because%20earlier%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20directed%20the%20government%20to%20come%20up%20with%20data%20and%20there%20was%20never%20any%20data%20as%20it%20%5Bmob%20lynching%5D%C2%A0%20was%20not%20defined.%20Now%20at%20least%20there%20is%20the%20provision%20to%20have%20that%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20also%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Government%20just%20introduced%203%20bills%20to%20completely%20overhaul%20and%20replace%20the%20core%20of%20Indian%20criminal%20law.%20No%20consultation.%20No%20discussion.%20No%20chance%20for%20any%20experts%20to%20review%20them.%20Heaven%20help%20us%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Vakasha%20Sachdev%20(%40VakashaS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVakashaS%2Fstatus%2F1689944564931633152%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBREAKING%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BREAKING%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Home%20Minister%20introduces%20bill%20to%20amend%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%2C%20and%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20are%20sought%20to%20be%20changed%2C%20from%20English%20to%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%3E%20IPC%20to%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%3E%20CrPC%20to%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSLzgo4tj9Z%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSLzgo4tj9Z%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Saurav%20Das%20(%40OfficialSauravD)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOfficialSauravD%2Fstatus%2F1689901586166980608%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Hindi%20Imposition%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20have%20also%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20nomenclature%20of%20the%20new%20legislations%20in%20Hindi%20as%20opposed%20to%20English%20as%20in%20other%20laws.%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20P.%20Wilson%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20this%20was%20another%20form%20of%20Hindi%20imposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShocked%20to%20see%20names%20of%20new%20IPC%2C%20CrPC%20and%20Evidence%20Act%20in%20Hindi.%20Maybe%20the%20Hon.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20has%20not%20seen%20Article%20348%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%3F%20Names%20of%20Bills%20%26amp%3B%20Acts%20must%20be%20in%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EShocked%20to%20see%20names%20of%20new%20IPC%2C%20CrPC%20and%20Evidence%20Act%20in%20Hindi.%20Maybe%20the%20Hon.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20has%20not%20seen%20Article%20348%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%3F%20Names%20of%20Bills%20%26amp%3B%20Acts%20must%20be%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20yet%20another%20form%20of%20Hindi%20imposition.%20South%20Indian%20lawyers%20are%20going%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTuXAjqpcdL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTuXAjqpcdL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20P.%20Wilson%20(%40PWilsonDMK)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPWilsonDMK%2Fstatus%2F1689976175572217856%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20yet%20another%20form%20of%20Hindi%20imposition.%20South%20Indian%20lawyers%20are%20going%20to%20spend%20most%20of%20the%20time%20in%20courts%20trying%20to%20pronounce%20these%20names.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3ESanjoy%20Ghose%2C%20senior%20advocate%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20said%20that%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunheard%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20legislations%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20ordinances%20or%20bills%20have%20a%20Hindi%20and%20an%20English%20version.%20But%20this%20is%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20they%20have%20given%20the%20English%20version%20a%20Hindi%20name%20and%20forced%20a%20Hindi%20name%20on%20English%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20this%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20light%20of%20a%20very%20Brahmincal%20Hindi%20imposition%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20I%20say%20this%20is%20that%20is%20a%20very%20Sanskritised%20Hindi%20name%20that%20they%20have%20given%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20it%20could%20have%20been%20named%20simply%20%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Danda%20Kosh%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Efor%20instance%20but%20instead%20it%20is%20called%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20Sanskritised%20Hindi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhose%20added%20that%20it%20is%20also%20not%20clear%20why%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20bring%20in%20entirely%20new%20laws%20instead%20of%20simply%20bringing%20in%20amendments.%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20these%20are%20colonial%20legislations.%20But%20other%20nations%20like%20Malaysia%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20etc.%2C%20have%20also%20continued%20with%20the%20same%20penal%20code.%20Why%20is%20there%20a%20need%20to%20replace%20it%20entirely%20instead%20of%20bringing%20in%20amendments%3F%E2%80%9DAshwani%20Kumar%2C%20senior%20advocate%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20for%20Law%20and%20Justice%20said%20that%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20law%20%E2%80%9Cwere%20prompted%20by%20judgments%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20appreciation%20of%20their%20need.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20changes%20in%20law%20relating%20to%20sedition%2C%20mob%20lynching%20and%20crimes%20against%20minors%20and%20women%20are%20welcome%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20comprehensive%20law%20against%20custodial%20torture%20to%20address%20its%20several%20dimensions%20is%20not%20understandable.%20Hopefully%2C%20such%20a%20law%20will%20be%20introduced%20soon%20in%20furtherance%20of%20the%20right%20to%20dignity%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691760169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09222428%2FAmit-Anil-Chandra-Shah-in-Lok-Sabha.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20sedition%20law%20has%20been%20'repealed'%2C%20it%20appears%20only%20the%20word%20'sedition'%20may%20have%20been%20dropped%2C%20for%20the%20law%20remains%20and%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20has%20been%20made%20more%20draconian.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sedition%20Law%20'Repealed'%3B%20Three%20New%20Bills%20Tabled%20in%20Parliament%20to%20Replace%20Criminal%20Laws%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09222428%2FAmit-Anil-Chandra-Shah-in-Lok-Sabha.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Friday%20(August%2011)%20announced%20in%20parliament%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Crepeal%E2%80%9D%20the%20sedition%20law%2C%20as%20he%20introduced%20three%20new%20Bills%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20a%20move%20to%20reform%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20and%20shed%20its%20colonial%20legacy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20new%20bills%20include%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%3B%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201898%3B%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20British%20laws%20were%20made%20to%20strengthen%20and%20protect%20the%20British%20government%20and%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20punish%20and%20not%20bring%20justice.%20The%20spirit%20of%20three%20new%20laws%20that%20we%20are%20bringing%20will%20not%20be%20to%20punish%20but%20to%20give%20justice%20to%20every%20citizen%20and%20to%20prevent%20further%20crimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20gave%20a%20brief%20introduction%20of%20the%20three%20new%20Bills%20and%20said%20that%20they%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20and%20will%20be%20presented%20to%20the%20parliament%20thereafter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposed%20legislation%20brings%20important%20changes%2C%20by%20criminalising%20mob%20lynching%20and%20marrying%20or%20having%20sexual%20relations%20with%20a%20woman%20by%20deception.%20It%20also%20provides%20for%20compulsory%20video%20recording%20of%20the%20statements%20by%20victims%20of%20sexual%20crimes%2C%20imposing%20time%20limits%20for%20filing%20chargesheets%20and%20completion%20of%20trials%2C%20as%20well%20as%20conducting%20trials%20for%20criminals%20who%20are%20absconding%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESedition%20replaced%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98draconian%E2%80%99%20provision%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20important%20change%2C%20however%2C%20as%20hailed%20by%20Shah%2C%20has%20been%20to%20drop%20the%20provision%20of%20sedition%20under%20Section%20124A%20of%20the%20IPC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSedition%20(law)%20was%20brought%20(by%20the%20British)%20to%20save%20their%20rule.%20We%20have%20taken%20the%20historic%20decision%20to%20repeal%20sedition%20completely.%20This%20is%20a%20democracy%2C%20everyone%20has%20the%20right%20to%20speak%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20look%20at%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2Fthe-bharatiya-nyaya-sanhita-2023-485731.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Section%20150%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%202023%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eshows%20that%20while%20the%20word%20sedition%20may%20have%20been%20removed%2C%20the%20law%20remains%20and%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20has%20been%20made%20more%20draconian%20by%20making%20it%20punishable%20with%20imprisonment%20for%20life%20or%20seven%20years%20imprisonment%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESection%20150%20details%20Acts%20endangering%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20unity%2C%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%2C%20purposely%20or%20knowingly%2C%20by%20words%2C%20either%20spoken%20or%20written%2C%20or%20by%20signs%2C%20or%20by%20visible%20representation%2C%20or%20by%20electronic%20communication%20or%20by%20use%20of%20financial%20mean%2C%20or%20otherwise%2C%20excites%20or%20attempts%20to%20excite%2C%20secession%20or%20armed%20rebellion%20or%20subversive%20activities%2C%20or%20encourages%20feelings%20of%20separatist%20activities%20or%20endangers%20sovereignty%20or%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%3B%20or%20indulges%20in%20or%20commits%20any%20such%20act%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20for%20life%20or%20with%20imprisonment%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20seven%20years%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20explanation%20of%20the%20section%20states%20the%20following%3A%20%E2%80%9CComments%20expressing%20disapprobation%20of%20the%20measures%2C%20or%20administrative%20or%20other%20action%20of%20the%20Government%20with%20a%20view%20to%20obtain%20their%20alteration%20by%20lawful%20means%20without%20exciting%20or%20attempting%20to%20excite%20the%20activities%20referred%20to%20in%20this%20section.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20Sedition%20law%20(Under%20124A%20IPC)%20had%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%20by%20words%2C%20either%20spoken%20or%20written%2C%20or%20by%20signs%2C%20or%20by%20visible%20representation%2C%20or%20otherwise%2C%20brings%20or%20attempts%20to%20bring%20into%20hatred%20or%20contempt%2C%20or%20excites%20or%20attempts%20to%20excite%20disaffection%20towards%2C%20the%20Government%20established%20by%20law%20in%203%5BIndia%5D%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%205%5Bimprisonment%20for%20life%5D%2C%20to%20which%20fine%20may%20be%20added%2C%20or%20with%20imprisonment%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20three%20years%2C%20to%20which%20fine%20may%20be%20added%2C%20or%20with%20fine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20explanation%2C%20the%20law%20defined%20the%20expression%20%E2%80%9Cdisaffection%E2%80%9D%20as%20including%20disloyalty%20and%20all%20feelings%20of%20enmity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Section%20also%20explained%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccomments%20expressing%20disapprobation%20of%20the%20measures%20of%20the%20Government%20with%20a%20view%20to%20obtain%20their%20alteration%20by%20lawful%20means%2C%20without%20exciting%20or%20attempting%20to%20excite%20hatred%2C%20contempt%20or%20disaffection%2C%20do%20not%20constitute%20an%20offence%20under%20this%20section.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20further%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccomments%20expressing%20disapprobation%20of%20the%20administrative%20or%20other%20action%20of%20the%20Government%20without%20exciting%20or%20attempting%20to%20excite%20hatred%2C%20contempt%20or%20disaffection%2C%20do%20not%20constitute%20an%20offence%20under%20this%20section.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EAnas%20Tanwir%2C%20advocate%20on%20record%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20founder%20of%20Indian%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20said%20that%20the%20explanation%20under%20Section%20150%20of%20the%20new%20law%20is%20%E2%80%9Cincomplete%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20removed%20sedition%2C%20it%20makes%20a%20far%20more%20draconian%20provision.%20The%20explanation%20of%20the%20law%20appears%20incomplete.%20And%20it%20brings%20into%20its%20purview%20the%20potential%20to%20criminalise%20protest%20against%20any%20law%20or%20any%20action%20that%20the%20govt%20does%20not%20deem%20fit%20by%20using%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98subversive%20activity%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20a%20very%20vague%20term%20and%20can%20include%20anything%2C%20even%20a%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20offences%20and%20stricter%20punishments%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20said%20that%20in%20recent%20years%20there%20has%20been%20talk%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20law%20for%20mob%20lynching%20which%20has%20been%20addressed%20in%20the%20new%20legislation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20has%20been%20said%20about%20mob%20lynching%20in%20the%20last%20seven%20years.%20Now%20mob%20lynching%20will%20have%20a%20punishment%20of%20seven%20years%20imprisonment%20or%20for%20life%20or%20death%20penalty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20added%20that%20in%20cases%20of%20gang%20rape%2C%20punishment%20has%20been%20increased%20and%20may%20now%20include%2020-year%20imprisonment%20as%20well%20as%20imprisonment%20for%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20involving%20girls%20less%20than%2018%20years%20old%2C%20provision%20of%20capital%20punishment%20has%20been%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20absconding%20criminals%20like%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%2C%20Shah%20said%20provisions%20have%20been%20made%20to%20hold%20trials%20in%20absentia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20cases%2C%20people%20like%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20would%20commit%20crimes%20and%20run%20away.%20Now%20trials%20will%20take%20place%20despite%20their%20absence.%20If%20they%20have%20to%20appeal%20against%20the%20judgment%2C%20then%20they%20have%20to%20come%20to%20India%20and%20then%20appeal%20to%20Indian%20courts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20cases%20of%20criminals%20who%20have%20political%20clout%20and%20remission%20of%20their%20sentences%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20be%20let%20go%E2%80%9D%20as%20was%20seen%20in%20Bihar%20recently%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-did-the-bihar-govt-change-remission-rules-to-aid-the-release-of-convicted-killer-anand-mohan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealluding%20to%20the%20release%20of%20Anand%20Mohan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20account%20of%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20heft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20sentence%20can%20be%20remitted%20from%20death%20to%20life%20imprisonment%2C%20life%20imprisonment%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20seven%20years%20to%20three%20years.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20political%20connections%20will%20not%20be%20let%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20a%20separate%20category%20of%20crime%20has%20been%20brought%20for%20marrying%20or%20having%20sexual%20relations%20with%20a%20woman%20by%20deception%20or%20wrong%20credentials%2C%20as%20well%20as%20snatching%20which%20was%20not%20defined%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20laws%20will%20also%20make%20it%20compulsory%20for%20the%20police%20to%20record%20video%20statements%20of%20a%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20abuse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20order%20to%20streamline%20the%20trial%20and%20chargesheeting%20process%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20a%20time%20limit%20of%2090%20days%20will%20be%20imposed%20within%20which%20a%20chargesheet%20has%20to%20be%20filed.%20This%20deadline%20can%20be%20extended%20by%20another%2090%20days%20by%20courts%20but%20after%20180%20days%20the%20case%20will%20have%20to%20go%20to%20trial.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20arguments%20conclude%2C%20judgments%20have%20to%20be%20given%20by%20courts%20within%2030%20days.%20Judgments%20will%20also%20have%20to%20be%20uploaded%20within%20seven%20days%20so%20an%20appeal%20can%20be%20filed%20if%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOrganised%20crime%20has%20also%20been%20made%20a%20punishable%20offence%20and%20community%20service%20has%20been%20introduced%20for%20the%20first%20time%20for%20certain%20crimes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20order%20to%20bring%20accountability%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20force%20will%20have%20to%20provide%20documentary%20and%20digital%20evidence%20if%20a%20person%20has%20been%20arrested.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COften%20we%20see%20that%20the%20police%20after%20arresting%20a%20person%20don%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything%20for%20upto%204%20days.%20Now%20they%20will%20have%20to%20give%20physical%20and%20digital%20notification%20to%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20accused%20that%20their%20kin%20has%20been%20taken%20into%20custody.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20changes%20have%20been%20brought%20in%20to%20digitise%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system.%20Forensic%20evidence%20has%20been%20mandatory%20for%20crimes%20punishable%20with%207%20years%20and%20above.%20If%20a%20case%20that%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20over%207%20years%20has%20to%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20then%20it%20has%20to%20take%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20consent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20protect%20citizens%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKey%20features%20of%20new%20Bills%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20said%20that%20the%20three%20new%20Bills%20will%20bring%20important%20changes%20to%20make%20them%20relevant%20to%20Indian%20society%20and%20drop%20references%20to%20colonial%20rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20which%20will%20replace%20CrPC%20will%20have%20533%20provisions.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20changed%20160%20provisions%2C%20added%209%20new%20provisions%20and%209%20provisions%20have%20been%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20IPC%20will%20have%20511%20provisions%20against%20the%20356%20in%20the%20earlier%20law.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20changes%20in%20175%20provisions%2C%208%20new%20provisions%20have%20been%20added%20and%2022%20have%20been%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%202023%20to%20replace%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20will%20have%20170%20provisions%20instead%20of%20the%20166%20earlier.%20%E2%80%9C23%20provisions%20have%20been%20changed%2C%20one%20has%20been%20added%20and%20five%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Shah%2C%20these%20three%20laws%20were%20full%20of%20references%20to%20colonialism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20existing%20laws%20have%20references%20to%20the%20parliament%20of%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20provincial%20act%2C%20notification%20by%20the%20Crown%2C%20London%20Gazette%2C%20jury%20and%20Barrister(which%20is%20not%20there%20in%20our%20country)%2C%20Lahore%20government%2C%20Commonwealth%2C%20Privy%20Council%2C%20British%20Crown%2C%20Court%20of%20Justice%20in%20England%2C%20Her%20Majesty%20dominions%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20total%20of%20475%20references%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egulaami%20ki%20nishani%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(signs%20of%20slavery)%20have%20been%20removed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EManner%20of%20introduction%20%E2%80%98unfair%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20new%20legislations%20will%20overhaul%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%2C%20lawyers%20said%20that%20it%20could%20bring%20operational%20difficulties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20have%20been%20a%20wider%20consultation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tanwir.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIntroduction%20on%20the%20last%20day%20is%20unfair%20but%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20may%20consider%20amending%20rather%20than%20bringing%20new%20laws%20as%20there%20may%20be%20difficulties%20in%20interpreting%20provisions%2C%20bringing%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%20that%20the%20move%20to%20bring%20in%20changes%20like%20defining%20mob%20lynching%20is%20welcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20welcome%20move%20because%20earlier%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20directed%20the%20government%20to%20come%20up%20with%20data%20and%20there%20was%20never%20any%20data%20as%20it%20%5Bmob%20lynching%5D%C2%A0%20was%20not%20defined.%20Now%20at%20least%20there%20is%20the%20provision%20to%20have%20that%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691760169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Section%20150%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%202023%20shows%20that%20while%20the%20word%20sedition%20may%20have%20been%20removed%2C%20the%20law%20remains%20and%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20has%20been%20made%20more%20draconian.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsedition-law-repealed-three-new-bills-tabled-in-parliament-to-replace-criminal-laws%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Police%20File%20FIR%20Against%20Writer%2C%20Editors%20of%202018%20Book%20for%20'Distorting%20State's%20History'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29204217%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-05-29-at-7.07.45-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20filed%20a%20first%20information%20report%20against%20the%20author%20and%20two%20editors%20of%20a%202018%20book%20following%20a%20complaint%20that%20it%20tried%20to%20distort%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chronicle%20News%20Service%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Anglo-Kuki%20War%201917-1919%3A%20A%20Frontier%20Uprising%20Against%20Imperialism%20During%20the%20First%20World%20War%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20written%20by%20retired%20Colonel%20Dr%20Vijay%20Chenji.%20It%20is%20edited%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20assistant%20professors%20Jangkhomang%20Guite%20and%20Thongkholal%20Haokip%2C%20who%20teach%20at%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20Centre%20for%20Historical%20Studies%20and%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Law%20and%20Governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famp.scroll.in%2Flatest%2F1054175%2Fmanipur-police-book-author-two-academicians-for-allegedly-distorting-states-history%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20two%20FIRs%20were%20filed.%20The%20one%20against%20Chenji%20was%20filed%20on%20August%209%2C%20while%20the%20case%20against%20Guite%20and%20Haokip%20was%20registered%20on%20August%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20was%20published%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%2C%20filed%20by%20individuals%20from%20the%20Ukhrul%2C%20Imphal%20East%20and%20Imphal%20West%20villages%20alleges%20that%20the%20accused%20have%20disseminated%20falsehood%20and%20created%20an%20environment%20against%20public%20peace%20by%20representing%20the%20armed%20Kuki%20rebellion%20of%201917-1919%20as%20an%20Anglo-Kuki%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20says%20that%20the%20civil%20society%20organisation%20Federation%20of%20Haomee%20had%20the%20complaints%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainants%20have%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Manipur%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20there%20has%20never%20been%20an%20Anglo-Kuki%20war%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Kuki%20rebellion%20involved%20the%20massacre%20of%20Nagas%20and%20Koms%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%20and%20Meiteis%20and%20Muslims%20in%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20have%20been%20charged%20against%20section%20120%20(concealing%20design%20to%20commit%20offence%20punishable%20with%20imprisonment)%2C%20121%20(waging%2C%20or%20attempting%20to%20wage%20war%2C%20or%20abetting%20waging%20of%20war%2C%20against%20the%20government%20of%20India)%2C%20123%20(concealing%20with%20intent%20to%20facilitate%20design%20to%20wage%20war)%2C%20153-A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20residence%2C%20language%2C%20etc.%2C%20and%20doing%20acts%20prejudicial%20to%20maintenance%20of%20harmony)%2C%20200%20(whoever%20corruptly%20uses%20or%20attempts%20to%20use%20as%20true%20any%20such%20declaration%2C%20knowing%20the%20same%20to%20be%20false%20in%20any%20material%20point%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20in%20the%20same)%20and%20120-B%20(whoever%20is%20a%20party%20to%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20other%20than%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20an%20offence%20punishable%20as%20aforesaid).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20of%20Manipur%20has%20seen%20100%20days%20of%20brutal%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691758636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29204217%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-05-29-at-7.07.45-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-police-anglo-kuki-war-book-fir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20book%2C%20'The%20Anglo-Kuki%20War%201917-1919%3A%20A%20Frontier%20Uprising%20Against%20Imperialism%20During%20the%20First%20World%20War%2C'%20was%20written%20by%20retired%20Colonel%20Dr%20Vijay%20Chenji%20and%20edited%20by%20two%20JNU%20assistant%20professors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-police-anglo-kuki-war-book-fir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22K2%3A%20Climbers%20deny%20walking%20by%20dying%20guide%20in%20bid%20to%20break%20record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691758251000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FC37F%2Fproduction%2F_130774005_summit.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66471990%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Footage%20has%20emerged%20appearing%20to%20show%20Kristin%20Harila%E2%80%99s%20team%20climbing%20over%20Mohammed%20Hassan%20on%20Pakistan's%20K2.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1427%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66471990%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66471990.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66471990.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Journalist%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Typical%20Himachali%20Homestay%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20Sustainable%20Dream%20Where%20Guests%20Can%20Stargaze%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20journalist%20whose%20forte%20lay%20in%20writing%20about%20travel%2C%20culture%20and%20art%20for%2015%20long%20years%2C%20Sanjay%20Austa%20never%20fathomed%20that%20one%20day%2C%20the%20tables%20would%20turn%20%E2%80%94%20he%20and%20his%20journey%20would%20be%20written%20about%20instead.%20As%20he%20settles%20down%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20for%20a%20tete-a-tete%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20every%20decision%20that%20the%20Himachal%20native%20has%20made%20is%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300372%2F8-pocket-friendly-cosy-homestays-in-the-mountains-for-that-scenic-winter-break%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeep%20love%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20culmination%20of%20this%20love%20is%20his%20venture%20%E2%80%98Meen%20Bagh%20Homes%E2%80%99%20that%20he%20started%20in%202017%20as%20a%20step%20towards%20making%20eco%20travel%20possible.%20The%20sustainable%20property%20offers%20city%20folk%20a%20chance%20to%20live%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctypical%20Himachali%20home%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20surrounded%20by%20fruit%20orchards%20and%20farms%20that%20spread%20out%20for%20miles%2C%20all%20immersed%20in%20the%20glow%20cast%20by%20the%20setting%20sun%20silhouetted%20against%20the%20Himachal%20skies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-COVID%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20stark%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20homestays%20emerging%20in%20the%20state%20owing%20to%20people%20starting%20to%20prioritise%20cosy%20settings%2C%20homecooked%20food%2C%20and%20the%20experience%20of%20living%20like%20the%20locals.%20As%20an%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3ETribune%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322666%2Fretired-couple-turns-ancestral-land-into-eco-friendly-konkan-homestay-sindhudurg-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20homestays%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Himachal%20registered%20with%20the%20tourism%20department%20has%20crossed%20the%202%2C000%20mark%20as%20of%20December%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20face%20of%20such%20stiff%20competition%2C%20Sanjay%20has%20found%20a%20sweet%20spot%20between%20luxury%20and%20authenticity.%20How%20has%20he%20accomplished%20this%3F%20%E2%80%9CBy%20learning%20from%20the%20locals%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt6xJvquQWl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5