lement-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20international%20chloroform%20trials%20were%20held%20at%20the%20Afzal%20Gunj%20hospital.%20Image%3A%20The%20Deccan%20Archive%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20mid-19th%20century%2C%20medical%20education%20was%20picking%20up%20in%20Hyderabad%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20Hyderabad%20Medical%20School.%20The%20land%20that%20houses%20the%20OGH%20campus%20today%20was%20earlier%20home%20to%20the%20Afzal%20Gunj%20Hospital%2C%20which%20was%20constructed%20in%201866%20and%20served%20as%20a%20teaching%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20these%20two%20buildings%20that%20major%20medical%20breakthroughs%20were%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20malaria%20was%20made%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20Medical%20School%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F272865%2Fhyderabad-fever-hospital-sir-ronald-ross-nobel-prize-malaria%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENobel%20laureate%20Sir%20Ronald%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Afzal%20Gunj%20Hospital%20contributed%20to%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20anesthesia.%20The%20first%20international%20chloroform%20trials%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20sixth%20Nizam%20Mir%20Mahboob%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20took%20place%20in%20this%20hospital%20from%201888%20to%201891%2C%20and%20were%20conducted%20by%20his%20personal%20physician%20Dr%20Edward%20Lawrie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chloroform%20Commission%20conducted%20experiments%20to%20establish%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20chloroform%20as%20an%20anesthetic%20to%20treat%20patients.%20It%20was%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20that%20led%20to%20several%20lives%20being%20saved%20in%20the%20future.%20While%20the%20chemical%20was%20being%20used%20for%20surgical%20procedures%2C%20this%20trial%20helped%20in%20determining%20how%20it%20could%20be%20used%20safely.%20The%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20report%20would%20go%20on%20to%20be%